e.","index":316,"end_time":903.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":897.57,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"He did talk to somebody the.","index":317,"end_time":904.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":903.13,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Second time.","index":318,"end_time":907.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":907.18,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"All right, got it.","index":319,"end_time":912.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":911.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We just need to know why it didn''t show up.","index":320,"end_time":913.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":912.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Lindsey.","index":321,"end_time":914.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":913.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, it looks like we ran it through the workflow to format the phone number on the fifth at noon.","index":322,"end_time":920.94,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":914.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So if the call happened before that, it would not show up.","index":323,"end_time":923.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":921.26,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It was just before that.","index":324,"end_time":925.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":923.98,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Okay, it was 11am on the 5th.","index":325,"end_time":929.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":926.54,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"See what I have to deal with, Colin?","index":326,"end_time":934.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":933.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"See this bullshit I got to deal with?","index":327,"end_time":937.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":934.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you have to deal with this with us, with your employees?","index":328,"end_time":940.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":938.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Colin, we don''t even have phone numbers.","index":329,"end_time":943.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":940.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just meant in general.","index":330,"end_time":945.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":944.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I think every company has got their things.","index":331,"end_time":949.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t even have phone numbers.","index":332,"end_time":953.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":952.07,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I know.","index":333,"end_time":957.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":956.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And here maybe we''re hired the wrong firm.","index":334,"end_time":959.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":957.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Don''t even have phone numbers.","index":335,"end_time":961.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":960.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How do people call you?","index":336,"end_time":965.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":963.86,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":337,"end_time":966.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":965.54,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"People.","index":338,"end_time":966.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":966.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, that''s not a good sign, Colin.","index":339,"end_time":968.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":966.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You''re not selling yourself.","index":340,"end_time":969.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":968.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They don''t.","index":341,"end_time":970.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":969.54,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They don''t.","index":342,"end_time":970.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":970.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You have my cell phone?","index":343,"end_time":971.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":344,"end_time":973.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":972.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Guys brought up someone that had been filling out a bunch of forms from ads, even with different names and things like that.","index":345,"end_time":983.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":976.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I got insects, Right?","index":346,"end_time":986.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":983.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can''t directly just block them from seeing ads, but what we can do is take a few different approaches to reduce them from filling forms or even seeing ads a little bit.","index":347,"end_time":995.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":986.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what we can do is build an audience in Google Ads of people that have converted and try to pinpoint that person''s form fills so that they no longer see or click ads as well as monitoring for just suspicious patterns through Google from the HubSpot side.","index":348,"end_time":1011.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":995.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s really just upping the.","index":349,"end_time":1013.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1012.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The captcha and anti spam measures, which I''m not sure will have a full effect because their submissions seem authentic.","index":350,"end_time":1022.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1014.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''re just like, changing their name.","index":351,"end_time":1023.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1022.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, it''s not that big of a deal.","index":352,"end_time":1026.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1024.85,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So we are checking.","index":353,"end_time":1028.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1027.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, sooner or later, this guy will give up, right?","index":354,"end_time":1031.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1029.249,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''s what we hope.","index":355,"end_time":1033.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1032.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Unless he has, like, Nigerian prince money.","index":356,"end_time":1035.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1033.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, he''s probably a Nigerian prince.","index":357,"end_time":1037.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1036.53,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"Speaking of a Nigerian prince.","index":358,"end_time":1039.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1037.73,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That''S another great story.","index":359,"end_time":1041.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1040.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I gotta hear it now.","index":360,"end_time":1046.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1045.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, and it''s relevant to this conversation too.","index":361,"end_time":1049.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.98,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It was a lead that came in that seemed legit.","index":362,"end_time":1052.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1049.94,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We checked out the webpage and we doubt.","index":363,"end_time":1055.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1052.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We dealt.","index":364,"end_time":1055.619,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1055.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know, we''re like, all right, well, this looks like a real company.","index":365,"end_time":1057.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1055.619,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We start diving into it a little bit, and there''s like a bowl.","index":366,"end_time":1059.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1057.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The guy had, like, a crazy name.","index":367,"end_time":1060.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1059.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So then I took the, like, president of the company, and there was things in the website that made us think it was spam.","index":368,"end_time":1066.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1061.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Then we were pretty obvious it was spam.","index":369,"end_time":1068.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1066.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I reversed image search the.","index":370,"end_time":1070.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1068.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The guy who''s like the president, and it was like the Nigerian prince of trade in Nigeria was legitimately who that guy''s picture was that they stole and put in there.","index":371,"end_time":1081.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1071.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"People do anything.","index":372,"end_time":1084.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1083.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They only make, though.","index":373,"end_time":1088.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1087.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And this kind of goes to Ryan''s statement.","index":374,"end_time":1090.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1088.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, all you got to do is ask one additional question.","index":375,"end_time":1092.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1090.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"When they build these websites, they don''t go deep, so, you know, you only got to go, like one additional layer deep, and then the website falls apart.","index":376,"end_time":1099.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1092.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, but then you have authentic websites, like fixed caller id.","index":377,"end_time":1104.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1099.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s legit.","index":378,"end_time":1105.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1104.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, that''s so bad and almost you would have to believe it''s legit, right?","index":379,"end_time":1109.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1106.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":380,"end_time":1110.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1109.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, I can''t stop cracking up.","index":381,"end_time":1114.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1112.81,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"The dollar signs is what''s sending me the most.","index":382,"end_time":1116.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.25,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You just have to know that that''s pricing too.","index":383,"end_time":1120.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1118.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Dude.","index":384,"end_time":1121.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.2,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I just imagine there''s two guys.","index":385,"end_time":1123.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1122.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s like, I built the website.","index":386,"end_time":1124.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1123.76,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, dude, dude, that''s phenomenal.","index":387,"end_time":1126.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1124.72,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s like a conversation of dumb and dumber.","index":388,"end_time":1128.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1126.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":389,"end_time":1129.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1129.2,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Just when I think you couldn''t do anything dumber, you go and completely redeem yourself.","index":390,"end_time":1134.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1129.68,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They''re like the tab name.","index":391,"end_time":1135.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1134.48,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"How about dollar signs?","index":392,"end_time":1136.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1135.76,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"All right, next.","index":393,"end_time":1137.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1136.96,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Well, it''s our pricing page.","index":394,"end_time":1139.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1138.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Pricing is money.","index":395,"end_time":1140.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1139.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":396,"end_time":1141.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1140.96,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":397,"end_time":1143.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1143.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It looks like they just opened up notepad and went bracket.","index":398,"end_time":1145.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1143.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"HTML bracket closed.","index":399,"end_time":1147.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1145.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Funny.","index":400,"end_time":1151.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1150.8,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So we''re working on new headlines and descriptions for the MSP campaign.","index":401,"end_time":1157.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1153.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As well as the landing page.","index":402,"end_time":1159.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1157.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then same for the virtual phone system and IP like I showed on Pulse earlier.","index":403,"end_time":1165.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1162.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lindsey, for the spreadsheet that you sent over, we did split out.","index":404,"end_time":1170.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1167.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Actually I didn''t have this tab open.","index":405,"end_time":1171.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1170.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We split out into several different categories.","index":406,"end_time":1174.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1171.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":407,"end_time":1175.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1174.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I can send this over to you and then we''re happy to implement it or I don''t know if you would prefer to do it yourself.","index":408,"end_time":1181.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1176.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean if we.","index":409,"end_time":1185.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1184.68,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"As long as all the pages are ready to go, I can probably.","index":410,"end_time":1188.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1185.6,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I mean, you got hours to spend, Lindsay.","index":411,"end_time":1191.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1189.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So now.","index":412,"end_time":1191.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1191.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":413,"end_time":1192.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1191.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we more than happy to do it.","index":414,"end_time":1194.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1192.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":415,"end_time":1195.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1194.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":416,"end_time":1197.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1196.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Colin work for his money.","index":417,"end_time":1199.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1198.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, you guys do it.","index":418,"end_time":1201.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1200.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":419,"end_time":1202.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1201.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":420,"end_time":1203.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1202.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, perfect.","index":421,"end_time":1205.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1204.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":1210.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1209.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have it kind of listed here.","index":423,"end_time":1211.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1210.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the 1599.","index":424,"end_time":1212.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1211.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then the new phone systems landing page that we''re creating for the phone systems ad group.","index":425,"end_time":1218.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1213.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we wanted to test embedding a form directly on the page rather than clicking a button for a pop up or going to the contact page.","index":426,"end_time":1226.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1220.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if you guys are good with that, that''s the approach that we''re going to take on this one.","index":427,"end_time":1231.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1228.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep, I''m good with that.","index":428,"end_time":1233.61,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1232.57,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m fine.","index":429,"end_time":1234.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1233.61,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":430,"end_time":1235.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1234.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, well then we will split all those out and write all the copy.","index":431,"end_time":1239.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1235.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":432,"end_time":1239.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1239.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I know you guys were meeting to talk through some other campaigns.","index":433,"end_time":1243.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1240.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Two of the ones you had brought up was one was Stir Shaken.","index":434,"end_time":1245.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1243.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So going with, you know, caller ID authentication or call blocking type keywords for the search intent and developing a new page based on that is one approach.","index":435,"end_time":1255.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1246.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Text message approval support is the other one.","index":436,"end_time":1259.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So companies that are having a hard time getting their SMS campaigns approved, which would also be a new landing page that we would build with that.","index":437,"end_time":1267.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1260.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or we could also do a non branded pain point search.","index":438,"end_time":1271.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1267.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if you''re experiencing texting issues or call quality or drop calls, all these things and we could have a new page for that or build the two that I mentioned above.","index":439,"end_time":1281.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1271.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To split up in this campaign.","index":440,"end_time":1284.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1283.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think I''m out on the 2 above and I just don''t think there''s enough in the text messaging one to generate anything.","index":441,"end_time":1291.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1285.82,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And basically on the issue that Ryan and I are running down on a stake and Stir Shaken call attestation, it''s just so fluid currently, it''s even hard to talk about it.","index":442,"end_time":1301.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1292.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":443,"end_time":1302.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1302.14,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Because we can''t even get clear answers from people that are like connected directly to this stuff.","index":444,"end_time":1306.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1302.58,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And there''s a lot going on behind the scenes.","index":445,"end_time":1309.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1306.94,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"There''s a lot of adoption happening still.","index":446,"end_time":1311.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1309.26,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So we Might be a little bit early on it.","index":447,"end_time":1313.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1311.02,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, I agree with any kind of authority about it.","index":448,"end_time":1317.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1314.34,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So can we talk about this really quick?","index":449,"end_time":1320.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1318.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"While we''re talking about.","index":450,"end_time":1321.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1320.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Can we pull that.","index":451,"end_time":1322.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1321.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No joking manner.","index":452,"end_time":1323.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1322.58,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Can we pull that back up?","index":453,"end_time":1324.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1323.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That page back up.","index":454,"end_time":1325.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1324.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Does somebody have it handy, the website?","index":455,"end_time":1327.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1325.02,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''m legit on this one.","index":456,"end_time":1331.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1327.86,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I actually have a. I really want to.","index":457,"end_time":1333.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1331.3,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So let''s go to pricing.","index":458,"end_time":1335.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1333.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So.","index":459,"end_time":1339.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1338.83,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Because we''re talking about it.","index":460,"end_time":1340.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1339.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So here''s what I want to understand.","index":461,"end_time":1342.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1340.71,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like the only thing you can do nowadays to fix caller ID is you can go to the page and register it.","index":462,"end_time":1347.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1342.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right, Ryan.","index":463,"end_time":1348.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1347.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You go to the individual pages and register it.","index":464,"end_time":1350.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1348.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s really for only two carriers.","index":465,"end_time":1352.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1350.99,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It''s still.","index":466,"end_time":1353.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1352.63,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It''s really.","index":467,"end_time":1353.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1353.11,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You''re still only able to deal with Verizon and T Mobile at this point, correct?","index":468,"end_time":1359.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1353.71,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yes.","index":469,"end_time":1359.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1359.23,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"To answer your question, yes.","index":470,"end_time":1360.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1359.51,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s really all you can do.","index":471,"end_time":1362.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1360.83,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The other thing you can do is call attestation to make sure you''re.","index":472,"end_time":1365.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1362.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So basically we''re in between two methods.","index":473,"end_time":1368.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1366.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re in between the old methods, which is go the website and say you''re legit and fill out your form.","index":474,"end_time":1372.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1368.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The second, old school do not call type of theory.","index":475,"end_time":1378.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1372.81,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"The new way of doing it is call attestation, which is close, but it''s not quite there yet.","index":476,"end_time":1383.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1378.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And it''s really not end to end.","index":477,"end_time":1385.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1383.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t believe yet.","index":478,"end_time":1385.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1385.21,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":479,"end_time":1386.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1385.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean, we''re set up for it.","index":480,"end_time":1387.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1386.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, that we can send is going.","index":481,"end_time":1389.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1387.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"To be a whole other discussion.","index":482,"end_time":1390.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1389.13,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So.","index":483,"end_time":1390.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1390.37,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"No, not yet.","index":484,"end_time":1391.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1390.61,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So those are really the only two ways to fix the problem.","index":485,"end_time":1394.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1392.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So what they''re doing here, I don''t.","index":486,"end_time":1398.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1395.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I don''t even know what they''re doing.","index":487,"end_time":1400.21,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1398.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s kind of where I''m at.","index":488,"end_time":1401.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1400.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"This is bullshit, right?","index":489,"end_time":1402.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1401.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s because there''s nothing that we''re missing.","index":490,"end_time":1405.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1402.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Those are really the only two ways of doing it.","index":491,"end_time":1406.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1405.33,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We know both ways and we actually control one of the ways with our call attestation.","index":492,"end_time":1410.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1406.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":493,"end_time":1411.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1410.97,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re actually sending shit out.","index":494,"end_time":1412.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1411.57,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And we''ve still struggled.","index":495,"end_time":1413.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1412.69,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And we still struggle.","index":496,"end_time":1415.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1413.89,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":497,"end_time":1416.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1415.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":498,"end_time":1417.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1416.77,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Oh, here you go.","index":499,"end_time":1420.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1419.54,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Look at the bot.","index":500,"end_time":1420.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1420.3,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Look.","index":501,"end_time":1421.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1420.98,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right, look at miscellaneous right there.","index":502,"end_time":1423.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1421.26,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"If we cannot fix a carrier, your repair costs will be prorated.","index":503,"end_time":1428.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1423.54,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"So they''re even saying, like they''re going to go out there and do this that we already know about, Matt, and if it works, great.","index":504,"end_time":1432.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1428.1,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And if not, they''re going to say we''ll just prorate it.","index":505,"end_time":1435.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1432.98,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"They say it happens less than 1% of the time.","index":506,"end_time":1437.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1435.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, but that''s, it''s.","index":507,"end_time":1438.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1437.82,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s not true.","index":508,"end_time":1439.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1438.9,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It happens a lot.","index":509,"end_time":1441.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1440.34,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You still have to pay, though.","index":510,"end_time":1443.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1442.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"They''ll just credit you 20 bucks.","index":511,"end_time":1444.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1443.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Right?","index":512,"end_time":1447.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1447.02,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s.","index":513,"end_time":1447.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1447.22,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, if anything, this, this, this whole pricing page is just reaffirming what we think we know right now.","index":514,"end_time":1456.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1449.5,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right.","index":515,"end_time":1457.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1457.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So I guess that was my point of it.","index":516,"end_time":1459.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1457.66,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s very scammy.","index":517,"end_time":1460.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1459.18,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"The.","index":518,"end_time":1462.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1462.06,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The point of it, I guess was, is that this is tough.","index":519,"end_time":1465.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1462.38,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s a tough thing to get into.","index":520,"end_time":1466.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1465.42,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And, like, I wouldn''t want to make this guarantee that I could fix it.","index":521,"end_time":1469.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1466.98,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sure.","index":522,"end_time":1470.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1469.82,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And I think we know what we''re talking about, and we actually control the calls.","index":523,"end_time":1474.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1471.27,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"These motherfuckers don''t even control the calls.","index":524,"end_time":1476.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1474.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":525,"end_time":1478.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1478.63,"speaker_name":"Christopher Quigley"},{"text":"How much more can you do if you don''t really own the number unless you''re just registering it in these various databases?","index":526,"end_time":1484.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1478.99,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s about it.","index":527,"end_time":1485.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1484.39,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And we already know that that kind of doesn''t.","index":528,"end_time":1488.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1485.75,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know, and if a firm has a bad attestation rating, they can''t fix it.","index":529,"end_time":1495.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1488.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Unless they''re the carrier.","index":530,"end_time":1496.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1495.43,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They can''t fix it there''s just impossible.","index":531,"end_time":1500.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1498.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":532,"end_time":1501.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1501.08,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":533,"end_time":1502.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1501.56,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know, I''m on Verizon, and Verizon has noticed I''ve done a bunch of spam calls, so Verizon downgrades me to.","index":534,"end_time":1508.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1502.6,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I can''t even remember what level it is.","index":535,"end_time":1510.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1509,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Downgrades me on the attestation.","index":536,"end_time":1512.919,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1510.92,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''m fucked.","index":537,"end_time":1514.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1513.24,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, yeah, the fix its caller id.","index":538,"end_time":1517.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1514.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Unless the behavior of your call starts to look more like legitimate calls.","index":539,"end_time":1522.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1518.2,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"There''s quote unquote algorithms and different.","index":540,"end_time":1525.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1522.77,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know, even Isaiah started spitting out the.","index":541,"end_time":1528.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1526.21,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"To us just before this call.","index":542,"end_time":1529.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1528.61,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know.","index":543,"end_time":1531.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1530.61,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Each carrier uses its own analytics engine, which employs specific algorithms to monitor call metrics, industry databases, and attestation levels, among other factors, to determine the call labels.","index":544,"end_time":1544.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1532.77,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That.","index":545,"end_time":1544.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.45,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s coming from a guy on the inside that works for a major carrier.","index":546,"end_time":1548.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1544.85,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Right.","index":547,"end_time":1548.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1548.25,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"That''s basically saying we have no freaking idea all the things that go into it.","index":548,"end_time":1553.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1548.86,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"But we can.","index":549,"end_time":1553.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1553.3,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"We can put you in a pretty good position to have a good call rating.","index":550,"end_time":1557.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1554.22,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Don''t move.","index":551,"end_time":1557.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1557.1,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Don''t move.","index":552,"end_time":1558.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1557.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I get it.","index":553,"end_time":1559.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1558.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What is NFL Chiefs.","index":554,"end_time":1561.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1559.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, they''re saying they fixed this for the Chiefs.","index":555,"end_time":1564.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1562.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And their.","index":556,"end_time":1567.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1566.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Their testimonial was.","index":557,"end_time":1568.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1567.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":558,"end_time":1569.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1568.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, wait, wait.","index":559,"end_time":1570.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1569.14,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Go back to that.","index":560,"end_time":1570.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1570.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Stop this.","index":561,"end_time":1575.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1574.38,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"This page is gold.","index":562,"end_time":1576.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1575.75,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"It is.","index":563,"end_time":1577.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1577.35,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I just looked up one of their references on hold.","index":564,"end_time":1580.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1577.95,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Marketing.","index":565,"end_time":1581.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1580.39,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Seems to be a real company.","index":566,"end_time":1584.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1583.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":567,"end_time":1588.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1587.99,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Somehow I don''t think the Chiefs realize that they''re being used as a reference here.","index":568,"end_time":1592.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1588.35,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"