ut they''re.","index":599,"end_time":1647.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1645.1,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"They''re using, like.","index":600,"end_time":1648.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1647.18,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":601,"end_time":1648.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1648.1,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"They''re using.","index":602,"end_time":1649.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1648.66,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yes.","index":603,"end_time":1649.58,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1649.1,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s, like, kind of legit, but not really.","index":604,"end_time":1652.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1649.58,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And nobody''s going to challenge it because the guy is not even.","index":605,"end_time":1655.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.5,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"The guy might not even be alive anymore.","index":606,"end_time":1657.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1655.51,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"All right, we can go.","index":607,"end_time":1661.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1660.55,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It''s just random websites.","index":608,"end_time":1663.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1661.43,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":609,"end_time":1665.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1665.19,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":610,"end_time":1670.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1670.469,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the Pain Point campaign.","index":611,"end_time":1672.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1670.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lindsay, you were saying?","index":612,"end_time":1673.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1672.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I just think there''s a lot of different ways that we could go with that.","index":613,"end_time":1677.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1673.91,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I should have looked them up in seamless, but we got to stop.","index":614,"end_time":1680.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1678.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We got to stop.","index":615,"end_time":1681.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1680.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Rabbit hole in this.","index":616,"end_time":1682.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1681.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If you guys want to give me some things that you think an angry person having a problem with their phone system would be Googling.","index":617,"end_time":1692.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1686.06,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I can record them and then see if we can see, like, what kind of search volume.","index":618,"end_time":1696.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1692.7,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You''re asking us?","index":619,"end_time":1697.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1696.46,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, just kind of ideas.","index":620,"end_time":1700.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1698.78,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Just right now, quickly.","index":621,"end_time":1701.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1700.14,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s really not my main campaign.","index":622,"end_time":1707.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1705.5,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The one I want to talk about most.","index":623,"end_time":1709.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1707.34,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, is the one you and I talked about.","index":624,"end_time":1711.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1709.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Like, how do I own everything?","index":625,"end_time":1712.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1711.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Three cx.","index":626,"end_time":1713.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1712.64,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay.","index":627,"end_time":1714.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1713.6,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yes.","index":628,"end_time":1715.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1714.56,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s my next thing.","index":629,"end_time":1716.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1715.2,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"In fact, look it, Lindsey.","index":630,"end_time":1717.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1716.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"What am I looking at?","index":631,"end_time":1719.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1718.08,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It''s sticky noted on my monitor.","index":632,"end_time":1721.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1719.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, I see.","index":633,"end_time":1722.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1721.6,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So I.","index":634,"end_time":1722.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1722.12,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do not forget how important this one is to me.","index":635,"end_time":1724.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1722.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Okay, Colin, I see your examples.","index":636,"end_time":1726.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1724.64,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":637,"end_time":1727.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1726.56,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":638,"end_time":1727.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1727.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I can send this over to you.","index":639,"end_time":1728.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1727.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That would be awesome.","index":640,"end_time":1729.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1728.96,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So we will go on to Matt wanting to have our three CX ads show up everywhere.","index":641,"end_time":1737.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1732.08,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"So yesterday we were messing around with this a little bit, and it seemed like the PMAX.","index":642,"end_time":1744.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1739.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Cost savings calculator ad was showing on a search for 3Cx.","index":643,"end_time":1752.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1746.63,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Just 3Cx, the branded name.","index":644,"end_time":1754.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1752.39,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"The search, the PMAX ad was showing up for us instead of our three CX ads.","index":645,"end_time":1760.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1754.71,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And we would like that to be different.","index":646,"end_time":1762.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1760.75,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We want to be showing our 3cx ads.","index":647,"end_time":1765.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1762.63,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Anytime they''re going to show for 3cx anything, it should be the 3cx specific ads.","index":648,"end_time":1771.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1765.92,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":649,"end_time":1773.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1772.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I checked into it and our team is still looking into it.","index":650,"end_time":1775.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1773.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So with you guys already talked about this.","index":651,"end_time":1779.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1776.4,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"She sent me an email yesterday or today.","index":652,"end_time":1782.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":653,"end_time":1784.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1784.16,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"And Lindsey, in your email you were accurate.","index":654,"end_time":1787.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1784.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can''t control exactly the keywords that are going on in a PMAX campaign.","index":655,"end_time":1791.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1787.24,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But there''s a few different approaches that we''re checking in to see how much we can basically bring in the scope of it.","index":656,"end_time":1797.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1791.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One approach is to set an account level negative keyword as 3cx but on the 3cx campaign, switch everything to exact match.","index":657,"end_time":1805.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1798.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The other is that we have to work through a Google rep to allow a negative keyword being added to the PMAX campaign.","index":658,"end_time":1812.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So here''s my thing, Colin.","index":659,"end_time":1817.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1816.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"If somebody searches 3Cx directly, right.","index":660,"end_time":1820.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1817.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And give you the example, we showed up like our cost savings, like switch to us, save money, blah blah blah.","index":661,"end_time":1826.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1820.65,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That doesn''t do me any good.","index":662,"end_time":1828.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1827.01,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":663,"end_time":1828.49,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1828.29,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I want to be like usage 3cx.","index":664,"end_time":1830.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1828.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We''re, we''re a titanium partner.","index":665,"end_time":1833.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1830.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"We are who you should be contacting.","index":666,"end_time":1835.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1833.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"That is a far more powerful ad for us than, you know, a generic ring savings.","index":667,"end_time":1841.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1835.41,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":668,"end_time":1841.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1841.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Bullshit ad.","index":669,"end_time":1842.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1841.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":670,"end_time":1842.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1842.53,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"So that''s where I want to get.","index":671,"end_time":1844.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1843.09,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And I want to own everything 3cx.","index":672,"end_time":1845.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1844.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I really want to own everything 3cx.","index":673,"end_time":1847.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1845.93,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":674,"end_time":1848.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1848.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So then the other approach that''s a little bit cleaner is to just re attack the PMAX campaign with more like 3Cx or just partnering with tech mode based language rather than the cost savings calculator.","index":675,"end_time":1859.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1849.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well that then that blows up that whole campaign.","index":676,"end_time":1862.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1860.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"It makes it all 3 cx.","index":677,"end_time":1864.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1862.69,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Right.","index":678,"end_time":1867.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1867.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So anybody else?","index":679,"end_time":1868.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1867.49,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":680,"end_time":1870.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1868.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I mean I can''t have both.","index":681,"end_time":1873.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1871.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I can''t.","index":682,"end_time":1875.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1874.45,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I need to get a Google rep on the.","index":683,"end_time":1877.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1875.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Because it has to go through a Google rep because it''s.","index":684,"end_time":1879.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1877.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, you got, you got to talk to a Google person live.","index":685,"end_time":1882.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1880.13,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you think there''s anybody who actually works there?","index":686,"end_time":1883.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1882.17,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, we get emails from them whenever we submit.","index":687,"end_time":1888.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1886.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''ll email like a week or two later in response.","index":688,"end_time":1890.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1888.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Ryan, when they''re talking to them.","index":689,"end_time":1893.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1891.96,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Do you want, Ryan, you want to jump on that call so you can talk about your, your Google issue that you have too?","index":690,"end_time":1897.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1893.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be great.","index":691,"end_time":1899.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1898.36,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"What issue do you have, Ryan?","index":692,"end_time":1901.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1900.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, it''s an issue in their Google Cloud platform with a quota amount where we need to increase a quota and you really just can''t.","index":693,"end_time":1913.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1902.6,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Like it''s okay, well we''ll get you in touch with you hit a certain amount and it''s like, okay, we need to talk to a rap.","index":694,"end_time":1918.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1913.47,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And then you try to set it up and it, you go round and round and round and it doesn''t happen.","index":695,"end_time":1923.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1918.27,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And you.","index":696,"end_time":1925.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1924.59,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s just, you know, you know how it is.","index":697,"end_time":1927.309,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1925.31,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, you guys dealt with a little bit.","index":698,"end_time":1928.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1927.31,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Matt and Lindsay, when you tried to work with Google, it was kind of the same thing.","index":699,"end_time":1933.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1928.87,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"They''re like, Colin, they don''t have phones either.","index":700,"end_time":1935.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1934.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, no.","index":701,"end_time":1938.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1936.35,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s how my Google support experience has gone for many years.","index":702,"end_time":1941.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1938.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"But if you think that you can get a meeting with a rep to be able to add the negative keyword to the campaign, I think that''s probably the solution.","index":703,"end_time":1949.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1941.59,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We just don''t want them competing with each other.","index":704,"end_time":1952.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1949.03,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"We don''t want campaigns competing with each other.","index":705,"end_time":1954.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1952.03,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yep, 100%.","index":706,"end_time":1956.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1955.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And right now what the PMAX campaign thinks it''s doing is outsmarting the search campaign.","index":707,"end_time":1960.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1956.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, I''m going to try that, but I''m not going to stop.","index":708,"end_time":1964.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1962.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re gonna exhaust all options in between now and then because again, we can''t control how quick they respond to get on a call or just make the change in the account for us.","index":709,"end_time":1972.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1964.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I like how Colin said you can''t control how long it takes to get him on a call.","index":710,"end_time":1976.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1973.23,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"He''s very hopeful he''s gonna get somebody on a call.","index":711,"end_time":1978.19,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1976.11,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Have you ever talked to anybody at Google, Colin?","index":712,"end_time":1981.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1979.63,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I have.","index":713,"end_time":1982.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1981.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They change people like every week.","index":714,"end_time":1986.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1984.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Were they American?","index":715,"end_time":1986.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1986.19,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"No, they''re never American.","index":716,"end_time":1990.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1988.67,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"If you think it''ll help, you throw in the email.","index":717,"end_time":1994.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1992.27,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Like, hey, like our clients are trying their budget but they don''t feel good about it.","index":718,"end_time":1998.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1994.31,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":719,"end_time":1999.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1998.65,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Always they''re looking, they''re looking to switch their budget over to Microsoft ads.","index":720,"end_time":2003.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1999.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Dude, threats always work.","index":721,"end_time":2006.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2005.21,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I mean, that''s not the worst idea I''ve heard thrown out.","index":722,"end_time":2009.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2006.81,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"How many C levels use edge?","index":723,"end_time":2011.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2009.37,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Too many.","index":724,"end_time":2012.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2011.69,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"That''s how I am.","index":725,"end_time":2013.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2012.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How many sales people use edge?","index":726,"end_time":2015.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2013.77,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Too goddamn many.","index":727,"end_time":2016.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2015.25,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Way too many.","index":728,"end_time":2017.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2016.65,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Resident user is not on this call.","index":729,"end_time":2022.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2020.01,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"It could be a good test.","index":730,"end_time":2023.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2022.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think I finally got everything from it.","index":731,"end_time":2027.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2025.03,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t hate this idea.","index":732,"end_time":2029.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2027.67,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I''ve never done Microsoft ads.","index":733,"end_time":2032.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2031.11,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''ve seen success with them for some businesses.","index":734,"end_time":2037.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2034.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":735,"end_time":2039.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2038.15,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"All right, let''s, let''s put that together a little bit.","index":736,"end_time":2042.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2040.07,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Colin will do.","index":737,"end_time":2043.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2042.03,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"I mean legitimately, a lot of C levels use freaking edge.","index":738,"end_time":2049.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2044.87,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":739,"end_time":2049.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2049.71,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Cuz it''s right on your computer like before you even buy it.","index":740,"end_time":2052.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2049.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":741,"end_time":2054.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2053.31,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"The other thing is, and it''s not now, and I think ChatGPT hit a delay with it already.","index":742,"end_time":2061.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2055.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But they will be rolling out ads on chat GPT.","index":743,"end_time":2064.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2061.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, I''m in on that.","index":744,"end_time":2065.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2064.75,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"You know me.","index":745,"end_time":2066.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2065.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I was.","index":746,"end_time":2067.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2066.91,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Can I have chat?","index":747,"end_time":2068.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2067.95,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Literally just gonna say that, like, how long until we have ads?","index":748,"end_time":2072.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2068.67,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"And.","index":749,"end_time":2072.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2072.15,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Sam Altman like put a pause on it because they were.","index":750,"end_time":2076.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2074.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''ve been having some fires this month.","index":751,"end_time":2078.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2077.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I see that.","index":752,"end_time":2080.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2079.08,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I''ve been following that a little bit.","index":753,"end_time":2082.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2080.68,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"I mean, it''s like the Facebook.","index":754,"end_time":2083.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2082.28,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They''ll follow the Facebook profile, Right.","index":755,"end_time":2085.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2083.56,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Facebook was free forever.","index":756,"end_time":2086.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2085.36,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Then they had this.","index":757,"end_time":2087.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2086.52,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Well, we''re going to start running limited ads and then, you know, shareholders start getting boners because they actually start making money and then everything, you know, next thing you know, now it''s all ads.","index":758,"end_time":2097.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2087.16,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Exactly right.","index":759,"end_time":2097.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2097.08,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"And repeat process, that''s for sure.","index":760,"end_time":2102.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2101,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, you get like five or six good years of something before it turns to ads.","index":761,"end_time":2108.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2103.3,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":762,"end_time":2108.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2108.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"As long, you know, I''m waiting for the moment where you can buy influence on chat GPT and that will be the end of it.","index":763,"end_time":2114.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2109.22,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, man.","index":764,"end_time":2115.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2115.14,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":765,"end_time":2116.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2115.82,"speaker_name":"Ryan Fisher"},{"text":"Sounds like a politician''s approach.","index":766,"end_time":2120.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2119.059,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":767,"end_time":2122.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2121.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":768,"end_time":2124.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2124.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Pretty soon you''ll make a search on ChatGPT and then you have to watch a 20 second like fake video game, like any app on your phone.","index":769,"end_time":2131.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2124.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s funny, Amari.","index":770,"end_time":2135.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2133.18,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They already got you microtransactioning, so that kind of works out.","index":771,"end_time":2137.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2135.26,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"They already got that part going.","index":772,"end_time":2138.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2137.74,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":773,"end_time":2139.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2139.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Especially when you use 11 billion tokens in a month.","index":774,"end_time":2143.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2139.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a lot of videos you''re gonna have to watch, Lindsay.","index":775,"end_time":2148.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2145.9,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Oh, no, just have a separate computer for that.","index":776,"end_time":2151.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2148.22,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"You know, just let those ad videos run.","index":777,"end_time":2154.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2151.98,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I know.","index":778,"end_time":2158.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2157.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think last week you mentioned there were some other conversations you were going to carry into your Wednesday marketing meeting.","index":779,"end_time":2162.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2158.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is there anything else out of that?","index":780,"end_time":2163.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2162.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, and before I forget, Lindsey, I don''t know if you saw the email.","index":781,"end_time":2167.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2165.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We did update the script to run on monthly budget, not daily budget.","index":782,"end_time":2171.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2167.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"