e a not right now more than like.","index":796,"end_time":2208.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2206.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, completely get rid of It.","index":797,"end_time":2210.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2208.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes, we talked about images for blog posts also probably being a no go for right now.","index":798,"end_time":2219.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2211.88,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Matt, was there anything else that you had that we haven''t talked about?","index":799,"end_time":2225.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2222.84,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"No, I didn''t write anything down because I thought I gave it all to you, but I don''t remember anything that we didn''t cover.","index":800,"end_time":2230.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2226.04,"speaker_name":"Matthew Look"},{"text":"Yeah, I think, I think that covered everything that I had written down here.","index":801,"end_time":2235,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2231.24,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''m excited to see the MSP campaign pages.","index":802,"end_time":2239.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2236.54,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"I''m excited to see the other new pages.","index":803,"end_time":2241.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2240.06,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Do you have a day or like an approximation when.","index":804,"end_time":2245.42,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2242.62,"speaker_name":"Lindsay Hall"},{"text":"Yeah, I was just showing the pulse at the beginning of the call.","index":805,"end_time":2248.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2246.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So MSP page will be designed this week and the virtual phone next week.","index":806,"end_time":2254.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2248.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, we need a.","index":807,"end_time":2255.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2254.7,"speaker_name":"Matthe