{"text":"Collaborate with Colin and Lindsay to align marketing campaigns and creative around 3cx messaging (43:26)","completed":false},{"text":"Participate in calls with Google reps regarding Google Cloud quota issues and PMAX keyword management (31:38)","completed":false},{"text":"Continue troubleshooting lead call logs and coordinate with Colin and Lindsay to verify and improve data accuracy for leads (14:21)","completed":false},{"text":"Support integration of marketing campaigns with call analytics and attestation understanding to improve caller ID fixes (25:57)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
