WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'a3899b64-d779-4aee-afbb-d43e2125ccf8',
    '2025-12-01 17:00:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KAXHDF9GPN0KRAKXM56T5NWX',
    'Baylee Gunnell and Matt Bernath',
    '{"Baylee Gunnell","Igor Zagradjanin","Matt Bernath | VITAL"}'::text[],
    890,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/82923011906?pwd=vgDbtA0sibPYnhqEB2QJH75nFuWVZP.1',
    '{"id":"01KAXHDF9GPN0KRAKXM56T5NWX","title":"Baylee Gunnell and Matt Bernath","summary":{"notes":"## **Website Navigation and Structure**\n\nThe team agreed to enhance website navigation by adding a dedicated services dropdown and expanding the learn section to improve user access to key content (01:09).\n\n- **Baylee Gunnell** proposed adding a **services dropdown** to the main navigation to organize clickable services cards, improving discoverability (01:37).  \n- The **learn section** will expand to include **Tuesday Coffee** and the **podcast**, renamed as \"articles\" for clarity and better user understanding (02:06).  \n- The goal is to create clear pathways for users to find tools, articles, and podcasts without confusion, supporting engagement and content exposure (04:01).  \n- This navigation update aims to increase time on site and content interaction, addressing user feedback about difficulty finding these resources.\n\n## **Free Tools and Lead Capture Strategy**\n\nThe team decided to offer free tools without mandatory lead capture to maximize user goodwill and organic reach, while using clear calls to action for conversion opportunities (03:57).\n\n- **Matt Bernath** advocated giving tools away freely rather than gating them, reflecting current organic marketing best practices (03:57).  \n- A dedicated **Free Tools page** will feature the two current tools prominently, supported by copy that “sells” the value of these tools to visitors (04:35).  \n- A call to action at the page bottom will invite users to book a clarity call to deepen engagement and move leads further down the funnel (04:52).  \n- This approach balances open access to useful content with subtle conversion opportunities, designed to build trust and generate qualified leads.\n\n## **Call to Action (CTA) Placement and User Flow**\n\nThe team refined CTA placement to align with complex purchase decisions, funneling users toward detailed service information before encouraging calls (06:39).\n\n- **Matt Bernath** emphasized using **Notion pages** as primary CTAs for strategic controller and bookkeeping services to deliver detailed, modifiable content supporting complex sales (07:09).  \n- The main CTA will direct users to these Notion docs, while a smaller secondary CTA at the page bottom will offer a clarity call for additional questions (08:18).  \n- This structure supports a layered decision-making process where prospects first understand offerings deeply before engaging sales, reducing friction (07:10).  \n- The team will implement links opening in new tabs to preserve user context and prevent navigation loss during exploration (08:42).\n\n## **Design Feedback and Image Strategy**\n\nInitial design reviews were positive overall but highlighted the need to improve image selection to better reflect brand and resonate with users (09:03).\n\n- **Matt Bernath** and Baylee agreed images need refinement, suggesting development of a document with **good and bad image examples** to guide future choices (09:43).  \n- Baylee will draft this document and have Matt validate it to ensure alignment on visual standards and brand messaging (09:59).  \n- Igor’s design work on desktop and mobile versions was well received, with minor layout questions resolved in favor of simplicity and consistency across pages (10:57).  \n- This image strategy aims to elevate visual appeal and user trust, impacting engagement and perceived professionalism.\n\n## **Operational Adjustments and Next Steps**\n\nThe team aligned on next steps involving design revisions, CTA updates, and leadership feedback to finalize website updates (14:21).\n\n- Designs will be sent for further review with adjustments to CTAs based on Matt’s insights about service ownership and commission structure (14:21).  \n- Matt plans to consult with Patrick to confirm strategic direction for the controller service page, ensuring alignment with current business models (13:42).  \n- Baylee and Igor will proceed with making the agreed navigation and CTA changes, integrating feedback into the next iteration (14:30).  \n- This phased approach supports iterative refinement and stakeholder buy-in, reducing rework and accelerating approval timelines.","outline":null,"keywords":["website navigation","services dropdown","lead capture","Notion pages","website design","call to action"],"overview":"- **Website Navigation Update:** Adding a services dropdown and expanding the learn section for better user access to content.  \n- **Free Tools Strategy:** Offering free tools without lead capture to enhance goodwill, with prompts for clarity calls to convert leads.  \n- **CTA Placement Refinement:** Main CTAs will direct to detailed service info, using Notion pages to aid decision-making before engagement.  \n- **Image Strategy Improvement:** Need to refine image selection for better brand alignment; a document with examples will guide future choices.  \n- **Next Steps:** Design revisions and CTA updates will be aligned with leadership feedback for swift implementation of website changes.","action_items":"\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nSend over proposal for website updates post-leadership team discussion (00:19)\nMake adjustments to CTAs on pages based on Matt’s feedback regarding funnel strategy to Notion pages (14:19)\nPrepare documentation with examples of good and bad images for website design validation (09:43)\nShare initial design drafts and incorporate feedback for image replacement and navigation structure (09:43)\n\n**Matt Bernath**\nReview and validate preliminary document on image examples to assist design improvements (09:43)\nPass the Elevate page design to Patrick for further feedback and alignment with current service management (13:40)\n\n**Igor Zagradjanin**\nShare design drafts via Slack and present desktop and mobile versions of Elevate page for review (09:43)\nConsider copy layout adjustments for subheadings on website pages to ensure consistency (11:07)\n"},"duration":14.84000015258789,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"id":1,"name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"id":2,"name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Yes.","index":0,"end_time":0.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":1,"end_time":1.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":0.72,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Happy Monday.","index":2,"end_time":2.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, Happy Monday.","index":3,"end_time":4.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Welcome back.","index":4,"end_time":4.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":4.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, same to you guys.","index":5,"end_time":7.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":5.92,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"How was the time off?","index":6,"end_time":9.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":8.08,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So nice.","index":7,"end_time":11.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great.","index":8,"end_time":12.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Great to spend time with some family and eat lots of yummy food.","index":9,"end_time":16.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good.","index":10,"end_time":17.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.2,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, same.","index":11,"end_time":18.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":17.84,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Good.","index":12,"end_time":20.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":19.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Good.","index":13,"end_time":20.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, we just had a meeting with Chris too.","index":14,"end_time":23.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.12,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It was great to.","index":15,"end_time":24.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":23.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"To meet him and just chat through just some.","index":16,"end_time":27.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Some website things.","index":17,"end_time":28.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":27.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we''ll.","index":18,"end_time":28.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.3,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We''ll send over a proposal on those details once I''m able to talk with our leadership team.","index":19,"end_time":34.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.74,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":20,"end_time":35.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":35.26,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"And then, yeah, we just had a couple questions about these new website pages.","index":21,"end_time":41.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We actually have some initial designs to show you too, so we can get your thoughts there.","index":22,"end_time":46.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.42,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Um, most of the questions are just related to, like, where is this going to live on your website?","index":23,"end_time":52.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":46.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So.","index":24,"end_time":53.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So do you want to add something to the navigation that links to all of these?","index":25,"end_time":58.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":53.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m guessing maybe a button on the home page too, because most of it''s already mentioned on the homepage.","index":26,"end_time":65.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":58.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, just want to get your thoughts on that.","index":27,"end_time":67.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":66.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":28,"end_time":70.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":69.51,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":29,"end_time":71.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":71.51,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"What do you recommend in terms of how people get there?","index":30,"end_time":74.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":71.87,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"I mean, initially this spurred from a conversation of those.","index":31,"end_time":78.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":74.43,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"I guess we''ll call them buttons, but they kind of look like cards.","index":32,"end_time":82.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":79.87,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"The services cards.","index":33,"end_time":84.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":82.91,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, the solutions built for you.","index":34,"end_time":86.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":84.35,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Having those clickable, I think would.","index":35,"end_time":90.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":87.95,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Would definitely be one option.","index":36,"end_time":92.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":90.75,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Do you think we should also have like a services drop down in the navigation or what do you think?","index":37,"end_time":97.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":92.83,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yes.","index":38,"end_time":98.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.79,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s actually, I was going to suggest that we.","index":39,"end_time":102.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":98.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, add a services here so those can drop down.","index":40,"end_time":107.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":102.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And on a similar note, I. I was going to bring this up at our last thing, but we ran out of time.","index":41,"end_time":113.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":108.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I also think we should expand this learn area and have your Tuesday coffee and your podcast living under there just so it''s easier for people to get to.","index":42,"end_time":125.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":114.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Got it.","index":43,"end_time":127.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":126.74,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"But yeah.","index":44,"end_time":127.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.18,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you have any preferences there?","index":45,"end_time":129.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.5,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"No, I think that''s good.","index":46,"end_time":131.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":130.26,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Right now when you hit the learn button, you go to like a learn landing page that has some tools and stuff.","index":47,"end_time":138.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":132.75,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So would we then have like, like, I don''t know, resources Tuesday coffee and podcast or tools Tuesday coffee and Podcast or what do you think?","index":48,"end_time":148.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":138.79,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Great question.","index":49,"end_time":153.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":152.67,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So we could keep this button that still just goes here and then.","index":50,"end_time":160.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":153.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Or yeah, maybe add like a. Yeah, Tools Tuesday coffee podcast so people can also get here and find these.","index":51,"end_time":167.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":160.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Or we could even have them go right to the.","index":52,"end_time":171.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":167.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Analyze my efficiency and calculate my leads.","index":53,"end_time":174.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s think this through from a, like, intention perspective.","index":54,"end_time":181.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":176.96,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So the tools, what happens when they click on the, like, efficiency calculator?","index":55,"end_time":188.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":181.6,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Do that.","index":56,"end_time":188.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":188.33,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Is that a lead capture?","index":57,"end_time":190.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":188.69,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":58,"end_time":191.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":191.13,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"No, no.","index":59,"end_time":192.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":191.61,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Or it''s.","index":60,"end_time":193.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, just this calculator.","index":61,"end_time":195.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":193.77,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Interesting.","index":62,"end_time":197.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":196.73,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So I wonder if.","index":63,"end_time":199.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":198.49,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Hold on.","index":64,"end_time":202.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":201.61,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"I wonder if, like, Free Tools could be a lead capture page where we talk about these tools and then when they click on the button to go to the tool, it captures the lead before sending them off to the tool.","index":65,"end_time":223.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":205.37,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Or is it more like.","index":66,"end_time":228.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":226.26,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t know what''s working these days in organic marketing, but is it better to just give people free shit and, like, hope they both recall?","index":67,"end_time":237.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":228.66,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay, yes.","index":68,"end_time":238.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":237.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I would give, Give, give it away.","index":69,"end_time":240.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":238.71,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":70,"end_time":242.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":241.91,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So.","index":71,"end_time":243.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":243.43,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So maybe that''s what we do is like Free Tools Tuesday coffee.","index":72,"end_time":250.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":243.83,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Now people don''t know what Tuesday coffee is.","index":73,"end_time":254.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":251.91,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So should we just call that blog or like, articles.","index":74,"end_time":258.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":255.27,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Articles, yeah, articles.","index":75,"end_time":262.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":260.79,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":76,"end_time":263.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":263.48,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So yeah, like Free Tools articles and podcasts.","index":77,"end_time":268.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":265,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":78,"end_time":268.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":268.44,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay.","index":79,"end_time":270.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, we can send this over to just to make sure we get the copy right.","index":80,"end_time":274.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":270.68,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":81,"end_time":275.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":275.16,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So then the Free Tools page is essentially this page minus that learn header that gets replaced with something like, you know, selling the tools.","index":82,"end_time":285.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":276.36,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"And then I think we just have the two tools below that right now.","index":83,"end_time":288.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":285.64,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Right?","index":84,"end_time":288.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":288.52,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":85,"end_time":289.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":288.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":86,"end_time":290.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":289.96,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yep.","index":87,"end_time":291,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":290.44,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then I think we should have a call to action at the bottom of this page.","index":88,"end_time":296.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":292.04,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"It''s like, hey, if you found this useful, you know, book a call to unlock.","index":89,"end_time":302.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":296.12,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, there you go.","index":90,"end_time":304.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.4,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay.","index":91,"end_time":304.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":304.12,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":92,"end_time":305.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":304.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is this good to leave this then, or.","index":93,"end_time":306.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":305.04,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Beautiful.","index":94,"end_time":307.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":306.76,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s perfect.","index":95,"end_time":308.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":307.24,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yep.","index":96,"end_time":308.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":308.08,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Okay, that should be good.","index":97,"end_time":312.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":309.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then just a few questions for, like, the next steps.","index":98,"end_time":318.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":312.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Once people actually fill out the form so we have that, they''re going to book a clarity call.","index":99,"end_time":326.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":318.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What?","index":100,"end_time":327.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":327.2,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Like, is this a calendly link we should use?","index":101,"end_time":330.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.08,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Is this the same form that''s already on your website?","index":102,"end_time":332.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":330.16,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, good question.","index":103,"end_time":336,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":334.96,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Let''s go.","index":104,"end_time":337.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":336.32,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Check that out.","index":105,"end_time":339.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":339.04,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, I feel like we should probably just take them here or have them have this at the bottom of that elevate landing page.","index":106,"end_time":353.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":344.25,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay.","index":107,"end_time":354.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I just put this to the bottom of the page.","index":108,"end_time":357.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":355.53,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":109,"end_time":359.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":358.65,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"It feels like it needs that copy above it too, though, right?","index":110,"end_time":361.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":359.01,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Like that.","index":111,"end_time":363.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.65,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, those two sections, like the video that sells the idea of the clarity call.","index":112,"end_time":369.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":363.61,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So maybe that is the bottom of that page.","index":113,"end_time":372.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":370.69,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we could do that.","index":114,"end_time":374.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":373.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":115,"end_time":376.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":375.17,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, we could just throw that there and then think same for the.","index":116,"end_time":382.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":376.13,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"This page.","index":117,"end_time":388.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":387.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I think.","index":118,"end_time":393.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":392.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, you just want them to go to your notion here.","index":119,"end_time":397.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":393.17,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":120,"end_time":399.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":399.02,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So.","index":121,"end_time":399.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":399.58,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"The reason that is.","index":122,"end_time":405.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":404.46,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Hang on, let me get back into my brain there.","index":123,"end_time":410.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":405.7,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"What was I thinking?","index":124,"end_time":415.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":414.86,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So part of the reason we wanted to go to this notion page is we''re.","index":125,"end_time":423.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":419.66,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"We''re moving to this, like, sell by doc kind of idea.","index":126,"end_time":428.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":425.23,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay.","index":127,"end_time":429.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":429.39,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And it allows us to.","index":128,"end_time":433.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":430.83,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So there''s two different.","index":129,"end_time":435.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":434.19,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"There''s two different calls to action on this page.","index":130,"end_time":437.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":435.03,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"There''s the.","index":131,"end_time":438.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":437.39,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"There''s the strategic Controller Services call to action, which takes them to the notion page.","index":132,"end_time":442.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":438.35,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"And then there''s the.","index":133,"end_time":