"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"So generate consistent referrals and then we have a column here.","index":230,"end_time":759.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":753.84,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":231,"end_time":762.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":761.84,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":232,"end_time":763.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":762.28,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So on all the four of these and also here, I''m not sure if this is consistent with like the.","index":233,"end_time":770.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":763.04,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"The remaining pages on the website.","index":234,"end_time":774.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":771.62,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"If I''m right, we generally like just have a subheading here and then the explanation.","index":235,"end_time":783.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.58,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So.","index":236,"end_time":783.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.46,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, whatever you suggest on that is fine.","index":237,"end_time":786.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":784.18,"speaker_name":"Matt Bernath | VITAL"},{"text":"Okay, good.","index":238,"end_time":791.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":787.94,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"And yeah, the.","index":239,"end_time":793.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.86,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"The mobile version and.","index":240,"end_time":805.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":799.95,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s it.","index":241,"end_time":806.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":805.63,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Any thoughts at the moment?","index":242,"end_time":810.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.15,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"No, I think it''s good.","index":243,"end_time":814.83,"speak