    'https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_MDUyZTNiYTMtMTMxNi00YWUyLWI0MjktZjNiZjI1NWU5MGMy@thread.v2/0?context={"Tid":"0188564a-93de-489c-bf54-1927d4a9ed28","Oid":"bdae9fd3-d481-4c5e-aeea-7272e37b7d07"}',
    '{"id":"01KBDRFNMC5WMCW4S78G8VZC5H","title":"iCorps + New North Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Account-Based Marketing (ABM) Setup**\n\nThe ABM campaign for Legal Services 2025 is on track for a Monday launch with full tool integration and lead assignment.\n\n- **All messaging sequences are live in Hey Reach and marked active**, confirming readiness for campaign execution (02:00)\n    - Operations loaded the full messaging sequence into Hey Reach, ensuring proper content delivery.\n    - Nathalie emphasized connecting Hey Reach, email, and LinkedIn ads for seamless lead tracking.\n    - The integrated lead scoring model will monitor contact engagement across all channels.\n    - Leads qualifying as highly engaged will automatically route into HubSpot and be assigned to Kristen for follow-up.\n    - This setup mirrors prior successful campaigns, reducing onboarding risk and speeding deployment.\n\n- **The ABM campaign will categorize all incoming leads as marketing qualified leads (MQLs)** to streamline sales engagement (02:20)\n    - Automatic lead assignment to Kristen ensures focused ownership and faster response times.\n    - Ruby confirmed no further questions, indicating team alignment on ABM processes.\n    - Nathalie plans to complete setup over the next few days and target a full launch by Monday.\n    - The coordinated tool integration aims to improve lead conversion efficiency and visibility.\n\n## **SEO Content Update**\n\nThe Boston page SEO enhancements are near completion with final edits underway to optimize search performance.\n\n- **Sam transferred the updated Boston SEO page to Jeff, who provided additional edits** for refinement (02:45)\n    - Nathalie will manage the incorporation of Jeff’s edits to ensure quality and alignment.\n    - The update aims to boost local search rankings and drive targeted traffic.\n    - Finalized content will be reviewed and sent back promptly to maintain momentum.\n    - This iterative review process supports continuous improvement and higher SEO impact.\n\n## **Timeline and Communication**\n\nThe team maintains a clear timeline with weekly progress check-ins to ensure milestones are met smoothly.\n\n- **Nathalie committed to updating Ruby as the ABM setup progresses, with a full launch expected by next week** (03:16)\n    - This cadence provides transparency and aligns expectations across stakeholders.\n    - Ruby expressed satisfaction with the quick meeting and current progress.\n    - The proactive communication approach helps mitigate risks of delays or misalignment.\n    - Clear deadlines support prioritization and resource planning for ongoing initiatives.","outline":null,"keywords":["ABM campaign","lead scoring","HeyReach","HubSpot integration","SEO update","marketing qualified leads"],"overview":"- **ABM Campaign Launch:** Legal Services 2025 ABM campaign launches on Monday; tools integrated and lead assignments set.  \n- **Messaging Sequences Active:** All messaging sequences are live in Hey Reach, ensuring effective campaign delivery and tracking.  \n- **Lead Qualification Process:** Incoming leads will be categorized as marketing qualified leads (MQLs) for rapid sales engagement.  \n- **SEO Updates in Progress:** Boston page SEO enhancements are nearly complete, focusing on local search performance improvement.  \n- **Regular Communication:** Team holds weekly check-ins to track progress and ensure alignment on project milestones.  \n- **Commitment to Transparency:** Nathalie will update Ruby on ABM setup developments, aiming for transparency and clarity.","action_items":"\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nIncorporate Jeff’s edits into the Boston page SEO update and send back to Ruby for further review (02:45)\nContinue ensuring the integration of all tools (HeyReach, email, LinkedIn ads) with the lead scoring model and HubSpot (01:20)\nOversee the setup and launch of the ABM campaign ''Legal Services 2025'', with launch planned by Monday (02:23)\nProvide ongoing updates to Ruby regarding ABM progress and confirm full launch status by next week (03:16)\n\n**Kristen**\nReceive automated lead assignments from the ABM campaign once launched (02:09)\n"},"duration":3.640000104904175,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"id":1,"name":"Ruby Pontbriand"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":12.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Hey, Ruby.","index":1,"end_time":15.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":14.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How are you?","index":2,"end_time":16.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":15.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m good.","index":3,"end_time":17.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":16.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How are you?","index":4,"end_time":17.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":17.28,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Good, good, good.","index":5,"end_time":21.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":18.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We don''t have to do camera today if you don''t want to.","index":6,"end_time":23.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":21.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":7,"end_time":24.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How did Thanksgiving go?","index":8,"end_time":26.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":25.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was good.","index":9,"end_time":27.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":27.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah?","index":10,"end_time":28.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":28.3,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, it was good.","index":11,"end_time":30.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":29.34,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Smooth sailing.","index":12,"end_time":31.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.22,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Good.","index":13,"end_time":32.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.82,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How about you?","index":14,"end_time":33.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":32.62,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, same.","index":15,"end_time":35.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.94,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I just had friendsgiving, but that was pretty smooth.","index":16,"end_time":40.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":36.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then on the actual Thanksgiving Day, I just relaxed the whole day.","index":17,"end_time":43.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":18,"end_time":45.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":44.46,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":19,"end_time":45.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":45.42,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"All right.","index":20,"end_time":47.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Will Sam be joining?","index":21,"end_time":49.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":47.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, no, Sam''s in Mexico.","index":22,"end_time":52.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":50.14,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Oh, right, right, right, right.","index":23,"end_time":53.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":52.71,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Well, he''s on his way to Mexico, I guess.","index":24,"end_time":57.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":55.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":25,"end_time":59.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":58.47,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That was for a wedding, right?","index":26,"end_time":61.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":27,"end_time":63.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":62.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":28,"end_time":66.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":63.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So quick update here.","index":29,"end_time":68.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":67.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So thank you for getting Kristen connected with Hay Reach.","index":30,"end_time":73.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":68.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I went in yesterday and looked and it all looks good.","index":31,"end_time":76.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It said it was active.","index":32,"end_time":78.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":76.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So one of our operations people went in and loaded in the messaging sequence into heyreach.","index":33,"end_time":86.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":79.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So that''s all good to go.","index":34,"end_time":88.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then now that we have all the tools done, next thing we''re doing is just making sure that all of the tools are connected for our lead scoring model.","index":35,"end_time":97.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":89,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''re making sure that Heyreach, the email tool, LinkedIn ads, they''re all talking to each other.","index":36,"end_time":103.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":97.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We have the lead scoring set up so that as these activities start happening, we''re keeping track of each contact and what they''re doing.","index":37,"end_time":111.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":104.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then they''re also making.","index":38,"end_time":112.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Our team is making sure that all of these tools are connected to HubSpot.","index":39,"end_time":115.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":112.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we''re going to do the same setup like we did for the other campaigns with they''re going to send into that highly engaged lead list over here.","index":40,"end_time":126.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":116.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":41,"end_time":128.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":127.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But we are going to assign them automatically to Kristen.","index":42,"end_time":132.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":43,"end_time":133.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yep.","index":44,"end_time":134.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":133.48,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then ABM Campaign will write Legal Services 2025.","index":45,"end_time":137.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":46,"end_time":138.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":138.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And they''ll all come in as marketing qualified leads.","index":47,"end_time":143.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":48,"end_time":144.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":143.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Great.","index":49,"end_time":145.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":145.48,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So that''s what we are working on over the next couple of days.","index":50,"end_time":150.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":146.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then we''ll aim for a launch date of Monday.","index":51,"end_time":153,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":150.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":52,"end_time":155.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":153.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Any other questions about ABM as we''re getting this stood up?","index":53,"end_time":159.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I think we''re good.","index":54,"end_time":161.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":160.41,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":55,"end_time":164.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Then update on SEO.","index":56,"end_time":167.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We finished updating this Boston page and then I saw Sam sent it over to Jeff and he sent over a couple more edits.","index":57,"end_time":177.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''ll work on making those edits and then send them back over to you again.","index":58,"end_time":183.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Cool, great.","index":59,"end_time":185.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So those are all my notes.","index":60,"end_time":188.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":187.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was a quick one today.","index":61,"end_time":190.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":189.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Anything else you wanted to discuss?","index":62,"end_time":192.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":190.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I think that''s it.","index":63,"end_time":193.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":192.74,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You''re right.","index":64,"end_time":194.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":193.74,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s a quick one.","index":65,"end_time":194.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":194.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":66,"end_time":195.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.14,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":67,"end_time":197.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":196.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I''ll keep you updated as we get ABM stood up and then by this time next week, we should be fully launched.","index":68,"end_time":205.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":198.1,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Hooray.","index":69,"end_time":206.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":205.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Very cool.","index":70,"end_time":207.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":206.66,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":71,"end_time":208.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":207.3,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Of course.","index":72,"end_time":208.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":73,"end_time":209.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":208.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Have a good one.","index":74,"end_time":210.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":210.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You too.","index":75,"end_time":211.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":210.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Bye.","index":76,"end_time":212.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Bye.","index":77,"end_time":212.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":212.26,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Bye.","index":78,"end_time":212.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":212.58,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"}],"dateString":"2025-12-03T15:30:00.000Z","host_email":"rpontbriand@icorps.com","meeting_link":"https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_MDUyZTNiYTMtMTMxNi00YWUyLWI0MjktZjNiZjI1NWU5MGMy@thread.v2/0?context={\"Tid\":\"0188564a-93de-489c-bf54-1927d4a9ed28\",\"Oid\":\"bdae9fd3-d481-4c5e-aeea-7272e37b7d07\"}","participants":["joe.michalowski@marketersindemand.com,mia.mixan@newnorth.com,nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,dallion.duran-ballen@marketersindemand.com,rpontbriand@icorps.com,sbagnall@icorps.com","joe.michalowski@marketersindemand.com","fred@fireflies.ai","mia.mixan@newnorth.com","nathalie.mi