Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, let me see if.","index":277,"end_time":773.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":771.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":278,"end_time":777.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, Lou, how about.","index":279,"end_time":779.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":777.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll send this to you.","index":280,"end_time":780.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Want to open it and see if we have anything before Roz leaves?","index":281,"end_time":786.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":781.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Can you not open that file?","index":282,"end_time":788.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That links file?","index":283,"end_time":789.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":788.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Does it.","index":284,"end_time":791.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":285,"end_time":792.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":286,"end_time":792.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So you can at least see everything.","index":287,"end_time":793.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s like PNGs.","index":288,"end_time":794.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":793.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, this looks like all of it.","index":289,"end_time":795.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":794.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":290,"end_time":796.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":291,"end_time":797.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":797.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So anyway, if you''re missing anything, obviously just let me know and maybe put a placeholder to kind of move things along if there''s something that''s missing.","index":292,"end_time":806.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":799.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But you should have Them all there from the.","index":293,"end_time":808.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":806.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The original file.","index":294,"end_time":809.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":808.609,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":295,"end_time":810.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":296,"end_time":811.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":811.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":297,"end_time":812.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":812.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But she''s super jazzed.","index":298,"end_time":813.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":812.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It looks really.","index":299,"end_time":814.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":813.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It looks really good.","index":300,"end_time":815.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we''ll.","index":301,"end_time":816.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":815.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll rejig, you know, the.","index":302,"end_time":819.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The rest of the sales guides with this new template, so.","index":303,"end_time":823.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":819.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":304,"end_time":824.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":823.61,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah, I think it''ll look good.","index":305,"end_time":827.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":825.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I might.","index":306,"end_time":828.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":828.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll have this all updated for you for when you get back.","index":307,"end_time":833.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, sounds good.","index":308,"end_time":835.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, sounds good.","index":309,"end_time":836.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then in the.","index":310,"end_time":837.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":836.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What I might do if I have a spare moment this afternoon, I might drop in the Info Print Manager current sales guide, and you guys can get started shifting that over to the new, you know, with the new title slides and all the.","index":311,"end_time":851.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Or, sorry, the title pages and all the rest of it as well.","index":312,"end_time":853.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":851.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":313,"end_time":854.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":854.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, because that''s next on my list of things, and I''ve.","index":314,"end_time":857.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":855.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve got it.","index":315,"end_time":858.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":857.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Got to get moving on some of this IPM stuff, so.","index":316,"end_time":861.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":858.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":317,"end_time":864.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":863.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":318,"end_time":865.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":864.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, very good.","index":319,"end_time":866.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":865.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I will endeavor to do that before I leave.","index":320,"end_time":869.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":866.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then you had sent me also the storyboard.","index":321,"end_time":876.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":871.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":322,"end_time":877.24,"speaker_id":1,"star