    '{"id":"01KBMXDAKEB5WP0KA2GP3E9QCC","title":"Agrippon // New North Weekly Connect","summary":{"notes":"## **Marketing Strategy and Messaging Alignment**\n\nThe team agreed on the urgent need to refine and unify Agrippon’s messaging across all channels to drive demo requests and better engage target customers (00:13).  \n- **Keenan** emphasized the importance of a clear, concise “hook” on the website and marketing materials that immediately captures executives’ attention, focusing on pain points and key benefits rather than long, wordy stories.  \n- He plans to deliver a prioritized list of **top one-liners and features by Monday** to guide website and content revisions, aiming for a fluid message that aligns sales decks, demos, and marketing collateral.  \n- The homepage will undergo a **facelift focusing on wording changes and selective imagery updates** rather than a full redesign, to incrementally improve visitor engagement and conversion rates (00:34).  \n- **Natalie** will provide the current library of outbound emails, LinkedIn ads, and landing pages today to enable Keenan’s review and feedback, fostering a working partnership with iterative, small tweaks prioritized for quick impact.  \n- The goal is to create targeted messaging sections addressing different audiences, such as executives seeking quick insights and billing staff focused on operational benefits, supporting differentiated calls to action like demo scheduling or needs consultations.\n\n## **Lead Generation and CRM Platform Evaluation**\n\nCurrent lead generation struggles center on converting high engagement into demo bookings, with only **one demo completed so far despite hundreds of clicks** (00:36).  \n- Keenan questioned the role and value of **Salesforce versus Zoho CRM**, discovering Zoho is the current CRM but limited by a free plan restricting contact volumes and email capabilities (00:09).  \n- The team agreed that the choice of CRM or marketing automation tool should depend on clearly defined goals, with readiness to invest if necessary for better outbound reach and lead nurturing (00:11).  \n- Keenan found no active Salesforce usage, and Zoho’s limitations led to consideration of upgrading or switching platforms to support scalable email campaigns and marketing lists.  \n- Access to detailed engagement data, such as website visitor tracking and email click reports, will be critical for targeting and follow-up; **Natalie’s team agreed to share this data**, including weekly reports identifying top engaged contacts worth outreach (00:43).  \n- Shane confirmed that leads generated from demo scheduling currently trigger email notifications only to him, and Keenan requested to be added to these alerts for timely follow-up (00:48).\n\n## **Website and Demo Scheduling Enhancements**\n\nImproving the demo scheduling process was identified as a key conversion lever (00:20).  \n- Two distinct **Calendly links were created**: one for a 30-minute needs consultation and another for a longer demo, catering to prospects with different time availability and intent (00:21).  \n- These links will be strategically placed in different website sections to target varying visitor mindsets and encourage action, such as quick consultations for initial interest or full demos for serious buyers.  \n- Keenan will send both Calendly links to Natalie immediately for website updates ensuring prospects reach the correct contact point without friction (00:25).  \n- The team agreed to incrementally roll out website changes in pieces rather than a big relaunch, enabling faster deployment and continuous improvement based on real user response (00:28).\n\n## **Outbound Campaigns and LinkedIn Social Media**\n\nCurrent outbound efforts generate clicks but low demo conversions, indicating a messaging or engagement gap (00:35).  \n- Natalie described ongoing **account-based marketing (ABM) campaigns** using email sequences, LinkedIn paid ads, and direct LinkedIn messages targeting dental industry contacts (00:41).  \n- A recent **free trial email offer** is being tested for higher conversion, and detailed click data from these campaigns helps identify highly engaged prospects for personal outreach (00:42).  \n- Keenan plans to review and refine LinkedIn posts, deleting overly wordy or ineffective ones and creating more focused content aligned with the new messaging framework (00:33).  \n- Due to technical issues with Publer and social account connections, Keenan will take over LinkedIn posting directly, drafting monthly social posts for Natalie’s review and approval (00:57).  \n- The team acknowledged a need to improve social media presence and coordination with other marketing channels to build consistent awareness and lead generation.\n\n## **Sales and Marketing Collaboration and Workflow**\n\nClear coordination between Keenan and Natalie’s teams will enable rapid execution of messaging updates and marketing improvements (00:29).  \n- Natalie’s team commits to a typical **one-week turnaround for new landing pages or email campaigns**, supporting an agile, incremental approach to changes (00:36).  \n- Communication will primarily occur via email, supplemented by the Markup tool for easy inline feedback on documents and drafts, streamlining collaboration (00:38).  \n- Shane confirmed minimal legal or compliance review is required on marketing content, allowing flexibility to quickly test and iterate messaging (00:40).  \n- Keenan emphasized maintaining message consistency across sales decks, demos, and website content to avoid confusing prospects and maximize conversion efficiency.  \n- Plans include reaching back out to previously engaged leads with updated messaging to renew interest and capture additional demos (00:46).\n\n## **Timeline and Next Steps**\n\nThe team aims to complete the initial messaging refresh and website updates by **Christmas**, enabling a strong start to outreach efforts in January (00:52).  \n- Natalie will send current marketing materials today for Keenan’s review, and he will deliver his prioritized list of messaging one-liners and feature highlights by Monday for website input (00:31).  \n- Coordinated incremental deployment of changes will begin immediately upon content alignment, avoiding delays from a full overhaul (00:28).  \n- Keenan will integrate with lead engagement data and CRM notifications to actively follow up on high-interest prospects, accelerating demo bookings and pipeline development (00:45).  \n- The team will continue refining outbound campaigns and social media posts as part of ongoing optimization efforts.","outline":null,"keywords":["Marketing Alignment","CRM Systems","Dental Industry","Lead Conversion","Messaging Strategy","Website Optimization"],"overview":"- **Messaging Alignment:** Urgent need to unify Agrippon’s messaging across channels to boost demo requests and customer engagement.  \n- **Website Improvements:** Focus on clear hooks and revisions rather than a full redesign to enhance visitor engagement and conversion.  \n- **CRM Evaluation:** Limited Salesforce use; exploring Zoho CRM upgrade for better lead nurturing and email capabilities due to current free plan restrictions.  \n- **Demo Scheduling:** Created two Calendly links for consultations and demos; links will be placed to enhance user experience and actions.  \n- **Collaboration Efficiency:** One-week turnaround for new marketing materials; clear communication via email and Markup tool for rapid execution of changes.  \n- **Timeline Goals:** Initial messaging refresh and website updates aimed for completion by Christmas to kickstart January outreach efforts.","action_items":"\n**Keenan**\nSend list of prioritized one-liners and key features with specific direction for website updates by Monday (31:23)\nReview marketing materials folder once received from Natalie and provide feedback (31:23)\nTake ownership of LinkedIn post management including deleting old posts and creating new content drafts (19:14)\nFollow up proactively with highly engaged contacts from email and website visitor data once given access (45:45)\nCollaborate with Natalie to refine messaging and website content iteratively (26:42)\n\n**Natalie Mintjens**\nSend all current marketing materials including emails, ads, one-pagers, pitch decks, LinkedIn posts in an easily reviewable folder today (31:23)\nGrant Keenan access to website visitor data and email engagement reports for deeper lead analysis (44:00)\nUpdate website contact/demo scheduling links with Keenan’s Calendly links (48:00)\nUse Markup tool for sharing marketing collateral drafts for easier feedback collection (39:08)\nContinue supporting parallel marketing projects with emphasis on prioritizing website and messaging improvements (28:18)\n\n**Shane**\nProvide login credentials and information related to Facebook account for Natalie to manage (59:16)\nShare current social media login and campaign information with Natalie and Keenan as needed (33:01)\nParticipate in podcast recordings and marketing collaborations as scheduled (51:31)\n"},"duration":60.7400016784668,"speakers":[],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":22.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good morning.","index":1,"end_time":24.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good morning.","index":2,"end_time":26.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":26.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How are you?","index":3,"end_time":30.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, good.","index":4,"end_time":31.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How was your Thanksgiving?","index":5,"end_time":33.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It was good.","index":6,"end_time":34.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Turkey was amazing.","index":7,"end_time":36.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I cook a turkey every year and I rotisserie it.","index":8,"end_time":40.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":37.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s kind of a smoked.","index":9,"end_time":45.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s really good.","index":10,"end_time":45.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":45.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How long does that take?","index":11,"end_time":47.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":46.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Normal time.","index":12,"end_time":49.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":48.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Good.","index":13,"end_time":52.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep, normal time.","index":14,"end_time":57.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":55.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So 350 degrees.","index":15,"end_time":58.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":57.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s it supposed to be, like 18 minutes a pound or something like that?","index":16,"end_time":63.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":58.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"16 minutes.","index":17,"end_time":64.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":63.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":18,"end_time":67.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":67.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know anything about that.","index":19,"end_time":68.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, you don''t?","index":20,"end_time":70.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you not cook turkeys?","index":21,"end_time":71.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Nope.","index":22,"end_time":72.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":72.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":23,"end_time":74.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":73.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, I''ve never even made like a whole chicken.","index":24,"end_time":78.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":74.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":25,"end_time":80.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":79.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you cook?","index":26,"end_time":81.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":81.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Are you vegetarian?","index":27,"end_time":82.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":81.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, but I just make like the individual pieces.","index":28,"end_time":86.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m not the best cook, so I just go for the simplest thing.","index":29,"end_time":90.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":87.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Very good.","index":30,"end_time":92.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":92.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":31,"end_time":96.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":95.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do we have everybody?","index":32,"end_time":102.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":101.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, Dave, I see you, Shane.","index":33,"end_time":105.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":102.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Can you hear me?","index":34,"end_time":106.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":105.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can hear you.","index":35,"end_time":107.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":107.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":36,"end_time":108.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":108.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But your name was.","index":37,"end_time":110.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":109.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I was like, huh.","index":38,"end_time":111.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":110.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re coming up as Skyler.","index":39,"end_time":115.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":113.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":40,"end_time":117.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":117.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":41,"end_time":118.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":117.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s unable to detect my camera for some reason this morning, so that''s fine.","index":42,"end_time":123.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":118.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So you''re.","index":43,"end_time":124.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I am here.","index":44,"end_time":125.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":124.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":45,"end_time":126.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":125.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is not Skyler.","index":46,"end_time":127.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":126.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is Keenan.","index":47,"end_time":128.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is Keenan.","index":48,"end_time":129.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":129.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":49,"end_time":130.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":129.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let''s talk a little bit about what we want to accomplish today.","index":50,"end_time":136.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":134.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Keenan, I know you have a lot of thoughts.","index":51,"end_time":140.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":137.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I want to give a lot of the floor to you and give that opportunity for you to connect with Natalie.","index":52,"end_time":148.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re super excited to have Keenan.","index":53,"end_time":150.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":148.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"He''s got such a great background and we''re excited for what he can do.","index":54,"end_time":154.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":150.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, and, and there we go.","index":55,"end_time":158.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now you''re Keenan.","index":56,"end_time":159.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, and Keenan, meet Dave.","index":57,"end_time":164.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":161.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Dave is our.","index":58,"end_time":164.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":164.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Account representative.","index":59,"end_time":167.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":166.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Natalie is marketing.","index":60,"end_time":171.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll let you guys introduce yourselves real quick.","index":61,"end_time":173.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":171.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Kenan, you can give us a little bit about drama.","index":62,"end_time":175.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Take five minutes and do that and then we''re going to talk about, you know, feedback, maybe some ideas for marketing in general.","index":63,"end_time":182.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Natalie is always, you know, if we want to know where things are, we can end with that.","index":64,"end_time":186.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I want to spend the majority of time with Keenan giving us feedback.","index":65,"end_time":190.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":186.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds great.","index":66,"end_time":193.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":192.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s nice to meet you, Keenan.","index":67,"end_time":195.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":194.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m Natalie.","index":68,"end_time":196.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ve been working with Shane on the marketing side of things for a couple of months now.","index":69,"end_time":201.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":196.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I don''t know if you''ve had an overview, but what we mostly do is a lot of outbound marketing.","index":70,"end_time":207.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So a lot of one to one emails, sending LinkedIn direct messages as well, and then also handling content like the website landing pages, sending out newsletters.","index":71,"end_time":219.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":208.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then right now we''re also standing up social media as well.","index":72,"end_time":223.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":219.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":73,"end_time":225.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":224.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''m David.","index":74,"end_time":228.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''M an account manager.","index":75,"end_time":230.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":228.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ve done customer success type roles a number of times and so.","index":76,"end_time":235.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":231.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So yeah, I''ve just been here a few months myself as well.","index":77,"end_time":239.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":235.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":78,"end_time":246.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":246.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, I''m Keenan, obviously.","index":79,"end_time":250.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":248.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is kind of my initial launch with everything.","index":80,"end_time":253.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":250.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I have a background in dental and with Verizon as well.","index":81,"end_time":258.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":254.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I ran the, ran the country for Verizon''s fleet launch a few years back and ended up with layoffs.","index":82,"end_time":267.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":259.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I ended up opening up dental offices in Utah.","index":83,"end_time":271.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":267.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We kind of rebranded, got them all onto one software and did a new launch for a dental company and ran a couple of other small businesses.","index":84,"end_time":282.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":272.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And now I''m here taking a look at this.","index":85,"end_time":285.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":282.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So one of the things that I''ve done historically is kind of go through companies where their current state is what things are working, what seems like it''s not working.","index":86,"end_time":295.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":285.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Take a look at marketing, branding and kind of bring all channels together to make sure that the message that we''re trying to deliver to customers in order to attract customers is fluid across everything that we''re doing.","index":87,"end_time":310.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":297.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I think that probably speaks the most to the research that I''ve done in reading and looking through the marketing data, looking at the website LinkedIn, just kind of where everything is at today.","index":88,"end_time":323.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s where I spend a majority of my time is, is making sure the message and the image we''re trying to create for a grip on is, is fluid across all platforms.","index":89,"end_time":335.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":324.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Cool.","index":90,"end_time":339.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"All right, Keenan, take, take it away.","index":91,"end_time":342.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":340.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m going to give you.","index":92,"end_time":343.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":342.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that okay, Natalie, if I give him the time?","index":93,"end_time":345.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":343.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":94,"end_time":346.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":345.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I didn''t have too many updates.","index":95,"end_time":348.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":346.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Only was about publer, but we can do that at the end.","index":96,"end_time":352.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":349.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, very good.","index":97,"end_time":354.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":353.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so let''s see if I can.","index":98,"end_time":360.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":357.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Share a couple things real quick.","index":99,"end_time":364.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let me make.","index":100,"end_time":364.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":364.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep, go ahead.","index":101,"end_time":367.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":365.099,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so this is kind of just a note board that I''ve taken as far as researching everything that we''ve, we have available to us today.","index":102,"end_time":378.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":370.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And some of this I don''t know yet.","index":103,"end_time":381.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":378.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there''s literally just questions on here for you guys to kind of find out where we''re at with marketing, what things we''re already doing.","index":104,"end_time":388.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":381.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this isn''t coming from a perspective of what are you doing?","index":105,"end_time":392.369,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":388.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because I don''t see it.","index":106,"end_time":393.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":392.369,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s.","index":107,"end_time":393.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":393.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What are you.","index":108,"end_time":394.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":393.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What, what''s happening?","index":109,"end_time":395.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":394.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because I don''t know all of this yet.","index":110,"end_time":396.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''m really just trying to get your feedback on, on where we''re at with some certain things.","index":111,"end_time":401.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":397.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Shane can answer some of these questions as well.","index":112,"end_time":403.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":401.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But in this initial kickoff, I think it''s important that we, even if things have already been said before, that we all say things in one sitting with all of us here so we can make sure that we''re aligned as we go forward.","index":113,"end_time":414.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":403.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And one of those things that I looked at as I look through data is some of the things you just talked about, Natalie.","index":114,"end_time":423.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we have Salesforce comes up in one area of marketing.","index":115,"end_time":427.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":423.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Are we doing anything specific with Salesforce today?","index":116,"end_time":431.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":428.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Should I be looking for anything there from your perspective?","index":117,"end_time":435.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":432.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, from the marketing perspective, all we use is Zoho as the CRM.","index":118,"end_time":441.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":436.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":119,"end_time":442.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":442,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Shane, as far as you know is Salesforce.","index":120,"end_time":449.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":446.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there anything specific Salesforce is doing for us today?","index":121,"end_time":452.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":449.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know of anything that they''re doing.","index":122,"end_time":455.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":454.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we haven''t used them.","index":123,"end_time":460.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":459.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":124,"end_time":461.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":461.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I just want to make sure I''m not supposed to be looking for leads or other information in there as well.","index":125,"end_time":465.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":461.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, we got to put you in Zoho so you can see all of our.","index":126,"end_time":468.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":465.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":127,"end_time":470.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":469.289,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I think I gave you that.","index":128,"end_time":472.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":471.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That link that.","index":129,"end_time":474.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":473.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So do you want us to use Salesforce?","index":130,"end_time":476.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":474.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is that what.","index":131,"end_time":477.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":476.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s kind of the evolving question, right?","index":132,"end_time":482.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":478.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if we''re.","index":133,"end_time":483.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":482.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re in this situation today, we''re not seeing a lot of leads coming in as we''re doing things right now.","index":134,"end_time":490.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":483.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s really the thing that we have to overcome.","index":135,"end_time":492.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":490.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do we start reaching more customers and.","index":136,"end_time":495.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":492.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And getting in touch with them?","index":137,"end_time":496.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":495.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ve kind of gone through a lot of the LinkedIn information and the.","index":138,"end_time":500.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":496.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I went through all of the.","index":139,"end_time":501.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":500.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The past comments and responses and, and LinkedIn from this perspective is very much like having a LinkedIn when you''re searching for a job, you get more people trying to sell what they can do for you than you.","index":140,"end_time":515.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":501.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re doing the leads.","index":141,"end_time":516.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":515.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And as I went back and I read through all of the emails that had come in the previous emails, through the sales emails, that''s what I saw a lot of on.","index":142,"end_time":525.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":516.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"On LinkedIn.","index":143,"end_time":526.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":525.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what I''m trying to find out now is, is there other platforms that we can be marketing on that may give us that instant connection in those leads and get people to start clicking on demos and things of that?","index":144,"end_time":540.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this is more of that 30, 30,000 foot view of what all are we doing so we can decide directions we go to.","index":145,"end_time":548.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":540.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there something that Salesforce can do for us besides being a CRM?","index":146,"end_time":552.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":549,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So Salesforce, depending on, you know, kind of what programs you have and what you do with them, they can provide leads.","index":147,"end_time":565.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":556.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if they have a dental vertical or a health care vertical within their platform.","index":148,"end_time":572.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":566.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There are times if you''re set up with them in a different way that they can provide some of that data that allows us to reach out directly to some of those companies.","index":149,"end_time":582.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I just really wanted to understand if we were something I needed to look at.","index":150,"end_time":587.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":582.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Your question is primarily around the CRM.","index":151,"end_time":590.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":587.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Outgoing capabilities.","index":152,"end_time":594.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":593.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, can you speak to Zoho versus Salesforce with regards to its.","index":153,"end_time":599.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":595.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Their abilities to reach out to customers.","index":154,"end_time":604.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":600.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it sounds like a.","index":155,"end_time":605.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":604.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What are those called?","index":156,"end_time":606.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":605.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"A marketing list or it''s.","index":157,"end_time":608.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":606.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If I''m capturing.","index":158,"end_time":609.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":608.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Keenan, your thoughts?","index":159,"end_time":611.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":160,"end_time":613.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":613.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it was more of is there something there today.","index":161,"end_time":616.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":613.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":162,"end_time":618.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"In Zoho, I think is what your question is.","index":163,"end_time":621.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Zoho versus Salesforce.","index":164,"end_time":622.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":621.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Really what we''re doing is comparing those two tools.","index":165,"end_time":624.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":622.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep, yep.","index":166,"end_time":625.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":167,"end_time":627.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As.","index":168,"end_time":627.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As far as I know, there''s nothing in Salesforce in terms of Zoho.","index":169,"end_time":632.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":627.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think Zoho is a little bit more limited than Salesforce.","index":170,"end_time":636.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":632.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And what we can do right now we''re on a.","index":171,"end_time":638.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''re using a free account for a lot of Zoho''s add ons like.","index":172,"end_time":643.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Zoho campaigns I think is one of them where we''re kind of limited by the amount of contacts that we can send mass emails to because we''re on the free plan.","index":173,"end_time":653.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":645.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ve also used Zoho surveys as well to do customer surveys where we were also limited.","index":174,"end_time":660.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":654.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think.","index":175,"end_time":662.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":660.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Shane, you used to use HubSpot, right?","index":176,"end_time":664.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":662.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the reason.","index":177,"end_time":665.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":664.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we, we''re.","index":178,"end_time":666.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":665.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we''ve transitioned from different CRMs trying to find the cheapest.","index":179,"end_time":670.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":666.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, HubSpot was cheap until it got way expensive.","index":180,"end_time":674.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":670.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Salesforce is actually very expensive as well.","index":181,"end_time":676.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":674.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Keenan, I think what we probably should do in this area is say okay, what should we accomplish?","index":182,"end_time":683.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":677.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Meaning what is the result we want to do in the methodology and then look at the tool that''s best best suited to do that.","index":183,"end_time":691.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":685.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it sounds like if I need to invest in order to accomplish that and there''s no cheaper way to do it, we need to consider that investment.","index":184,"end_time":700.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":692.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so.","index":185,"end_time":705.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that answers the question that''s really what I was looking for was is there something that I should be looking at today?","index":186,"end_time":710.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":705.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because as I''m in this research process and I''m looking at everything I''ve kind of just noted like I''ve seen a Facebook emblem a couple of places, I''ve seen a Salesforce mentioned in a couple of documents.","index":187,"end_time":724,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":710.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so are those things I need to be looking into, are they not?","index":188,"end_time":728.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":724.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so we''ll do that.","index":189,"end_time":729.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":728.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We''ll do that and talk about what we want to accomplish.","index":190,"end_time":732.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":730.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Exactly.","index":191,"end_time":733.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think that''s what we need to do.","index":192,"end_time":735.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And my suspicion is, is that you''ll say, oh, we need to do this.","index":193,"end_time":739.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":735.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''ll come back and we''ll have to invest some money and see if it''s worth it to achieve that.","index":194,"end_time":744.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"My suspicion is that Zoho would just tag on an extra fee for us, allowing us to accomplish that if we decide that that''s what we want to do.","index":195,"end_time":752.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":744.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":196,"end_time":753.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":753.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so to give everybody an idea of kind of where I''m at currently.","index":197,"end_time":760.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":755.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So whenever you put your information together, whenever we look at the website, the LinkedIn posts and how that ties into our demo, our pitch deck, any one pagers that we send to customers, there''s really some specific information that I really would like to see on those things as the key points to draw people in.","index":198,"end_time":785.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":762.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And some of those things, we have a lot of actually good information.","index":199,"end_time":789.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":785.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s just right now it seems like it''s in a lot of different places.","index":200,"end_time":793.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":790.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I''ve read through the entire marketing folder almost as far as the documents that we have there, the different things that we have that are customer facing, the things that we have that are case studies or internal or testimonials.","index":201,"end_time":807.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":794.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I started to note down some of those lines and some of that important information that you''d really want to have.","index":202,"end_time":815.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":807.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If you''re doing a pitch for a customer, you''re sitting face to face.","index":203,"end_time":818.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":815.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or on the other hand, if it''s an executive that''s having his coffee this morning and he''s looking through his, you know, his contacts or anything on LinkedIn and he sees something with a grip on on it, what''s going to make him click the demo button and actually offer some time to us.","index":204,"end_time":836,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":819.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so when we look at some of the documents and things that we have today, a lot of them are stories.","index":205,"end_time":845.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":836.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s more.","index":206,"end_time":846.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":845.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Longer.","index":207,"end_time":849.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":848.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Kind of wordy stories.","index":208,"end_time":852.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":850.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I''ll kind of give this example here.","index":209,"end_time":855.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":852.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so this document, while it serves a great purpose, there''s some small tweaks that I think if kind of input.","index":210,"end_time":870.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":861.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the reason that I wanted to share this, just to backtrack a little bit, we talked about fluid messaging, and that''s kind of how I started this conversation.","index":211,"end_time":879.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":870.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s really some key points that are going to draw those VPs, those executives, or even these billing people in that say, man, this is what''s killing me today.","index":212,"end_time":889.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":879.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do I fix this?","index":213,"end_time":890.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":889.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s worth clicking on, getting a demo.","index":214,"end_time":893.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":891.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But if they look at this today, there''s a lot of Words and we.","index":215,"end_time":900.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":893.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, you want to, you want something that''s a takeaway at the top.","index":216,"end_time":902.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":900.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":217,"end_time":903.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":903.149,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You want an instant bullet point that''s going to draw them in and say, okay, this might be worth reading.","index":218,"end_time":908.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":903.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Let me look into this more.","index":219,"end_time":909.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":908.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that really goes to everything, whether it''s the website.","index":220,"end_time":913.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":910.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Anything on there.","index":221,"end_time":915.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":914.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the website does have a pretty short.","index":222,"end_time":917.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":915.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or a pretty quick view on it where you have this blurb here at the top of the website that''s short and sweet.","index":223,"end_time":932.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":922.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There are some key things that I think are going to draw people into this more and understand what we do.","index":224,"end_time":938.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":932.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so the reason I have so many tabs up here and want to show you a few things, this view to me is extremely important.","index":225,"end_time":945.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":938.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This, this is a view that we can sell.","index":226,"end_time":948.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":946.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so when we look at the one pager, it has a lot of, has a lot of words.","index":227,"end_time":954.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":949.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It shows the report a couple of times.","index":228,"end_time":955.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":954.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But as a leader, if I look at this picture, this initial view on this demo, I know basically some of the things that this is going to do for me.","index":229,"end_time":967.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":956.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so this is a striking image.","index":230,"end_time":970.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":967.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I think some of the imagery that we''re using I think can be more effective to get a draw and then some of the wording as well, as we put it, towards just everything that we''re doing.","index":231,"end_time":983.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll be going through some one pagers and kind of throwing together some ideas and things that we can adjust.","index":232,"end_time":989.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":983.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But if I''m going to say, hey, I would like to do a demo with somebody and I get five minutes if I show them this page, this draws enough interest where they want to say, hey, wait, what, what is the 12 waiting responses?","index":233,"end_time":1003.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":990.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What does that actually mean?","index":234,"end_time":1005.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1003.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What does it do for me, the reporting and some of those things, I don''t think draw that as quickly.","index":235,"end_time":1011.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1005.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is the analytical.","index":236,"end_time":1013.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1012.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is the back end and what did it afterwards.","index":237,"end_time":1016.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1013.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, Keenan, I, I like what you''re saying.","index":238,"end_time":1020.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1017.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Give us an action plan.","index":239,"end_time":1021.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1020.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What do we need to do?","index":240,"end_time":1022.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1022.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like so step, step by step.","index":241,"end_time":1025.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1023.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And who needs to do that is your.","index":242,"end_time":1027.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1025.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is the other question that I''ll ask.","index":243,"end_time":1028.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, Natalie, my understanding is you''re.","index":244,"end_time":1032.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re going to be my point of contact for changes as far as website.","index":245,"end_time":1036.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1032.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then giving some, some direction on LinkedIn and what kind of ads we want on there.","index":246,"end_time":1046.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1038.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, so I mean, what I can do is so we have a whole library of things that are currently going out to people, so the website is one of them.","index":247,"end_time":1055.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1047.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We also have emails that are going out and LinkedIn ads that are showing.","index":248,"end_time":1060.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1055.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what I can do is gather everything and put it into a folder for you so you can take a look at it as a first step, maybe see if you have any feedback on those for us to adjust.","index":249,"end_time":1071.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, that would be great.","index":250,"end_time":1073.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1072.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if you can send that stuff over to me.","index":251,"end_time":1076.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1073.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What I''m doing right now is I''m gathering information from everything that we have, whether it''s marketing slides, sales decks, the website.","index":252,"end_time":1084.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1076.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''m kind of taking those key points and putting them in this list for myself.","index":253,"end_time":1089.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1085.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And what I would like to do first is align these fluid across those communications and pick out those key points.","index":254,"end_time":1098.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1090.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the information that I have, and I''m going to ask Natalie that you maybe show me some of the things that you guys have so I can get an idea of kind of the format and the platform that we''re working with as well.","index":255,"end_time":1110.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1099.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll have you do that in a minute.","index":256,"end_time":1114.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But these, there''s a lot of one one liners in here that we can use to draw some attention in some things out of testimonials and things like that.","index":257,"end_time":1124.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1115.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Without utilizing the full testimonial, we can kind of put that Cliff Notes version of why that customer was happy with the result that they received.","index":258,"end_time":1132.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1124.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then the demo is really where you speak to the specifics and what the tool does and what else we can do with it.","index":259,"end_time":1141.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1133.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But we''ve got to have that, that hook that initially draws them in.","index":260,"end_time":1145.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1141.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I think that''s a great first step if we can get all, all that information into one place for me to look at.","index":261,"end_time":1152.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1146.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m also just so everybody is aware I''m going to be going through the LinkedIn the past posts and making some adjustments to those things there.","index":262,"end_time":1164.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1154.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s a lot of words in there, there''s a lot of good information.","index":263,"end_time":1167.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1164.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s almost too wordy for you to be scrolling on a, you know, Wednesday morning and.","index":264,"end_time":1173.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1167.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or Thursday morning.","index":265,"end_time":1174.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1173.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the old post need to be deleted.","index":266,"end_time":1177.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1174.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":267,"end_time":1177.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1177.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so deleted and redone.","index":268,"end_time":1180.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1178.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s going to be one of the first things that I do.","index":269,"end_time":1183.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I created two calendly links.","index":270,"end_time":1186.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1184.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So as far as the website I know there''s a couple places where we have a demo and then on the same page see if I can find one of our pages.","index":271,"end_time":1199.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1187.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So there''s a demo here and then on a different page.","index":272,"end_time":1203.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1200.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So those are actually.","index":273,"end_time":1206.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1205.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we maybe we need to distinguish.","index":274,"end_time":1208.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1206.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the.","index":275,"end_time":1209.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1209.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"When you schedule that just takes you to a link to get.","index":276,"end_time":1212.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1210.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"When you click on the first one, it actually takes.","index":277,"end_time":1215.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1212.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You go click on the first one.","index":278,"end_time":1216.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1215.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I Don''t know if you''ve experienced this.","index":279,"end_time":1217.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1216.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Not that one.","index":280,"end_time":1224.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1223.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Go down to the.","index":281,"end_time":1225.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1224.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"To the.","index":282,"end_time":1225.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There you go.","index":283,"end_time":1227.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1226.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Scroll down.","index":284,"end_time":1227.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1227.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Click that one.","index":285,"end_time":1229.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1228.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This one?","index":286,"end_time":1231.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1230.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":287,"end_time":1231.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1231.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Then click that.","index":288,"end_time":1236.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1235.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep, that purple.","index":289,"end_time":1238.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1236.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s actually taking you through the system.","index":290,"end_time":1242.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1240.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":291,"end_time":1244.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1244.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what I''m looking for is if somebody goes on the website today and they go to book a demo, how they''re reaching us, that''s one thing that we need to update.","index":292,"end_time":1253.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1244.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is Monique''s today.","index":293,"end_time":1255.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1253.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It needs to be yours.","index":294,"end_time":1257.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1256.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":295,"end_time":1257.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I have a calendar.","index":296,"end_time":1259.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1257.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, would I be sending my links to you?","index":297,"end_time":1262.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, and then we''ll make that update perfect.","index":298,"end_time":1265.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1263.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I have those already created, so I''ll send those over to you.","index":299,"end_time":1268.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1265.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"My question on this is, there''s one.","index":300,"end_time":1273.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1271.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s a couple that say demo.","index":301,"end_time":1275.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1273.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"There''s one that says a consultation.","index":302,"end_time":1277.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1275.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Did we have intent behind those being different and are they different formats for calls or is it.","index":303,"end_time":1285.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1278.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re not different intents.","index":304,"end_time":1287.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1286.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":305,"end_time":1289.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1288.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I actually created two.","index":306,"end_time":1291.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1289.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the reason I did that is a lot of times when you''re.","index":307,"end_time":1295.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1291.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''re getting that initial interest from people, I created one that actually says it is for a needs consultation and one is for a demo.","index":308,"end_time":1305.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1295.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so you''re going to have two types.","index":309,"end_time":1308.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1306.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, you have two types of people.","index":310,"end_time":1310.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1308.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I would like to use both of those and make sure that that is clear when they''re on the website.","index":311,"end_time":1317.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1310.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So some of those people are going to glance at it and say, I''m not going to look at this right now.","index":312,"end_time":1322.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1318.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m just going to schedule a needs consultation.","index":313,"end_time":1324.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1322.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s a shorter window.","index":314,"end_time":1326.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1325.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it gives them that opportunity to say, I just have a few minutes to look over this.","index":315,"end_time":1330.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1327.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t have a full hour for a demo, so I''m going to send you both of those.","index":316,"end_time":1334.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1330.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, that''ll be one thing for the website and anything else we do.","index":317,"end_time":1339.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1334.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So whether it''s on, you know, LinkedIn or other marketing tools, I''d like both of those options to be available there.","index":318,"end_time":1346.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1339.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so would it be two buttons next to each other or would it be like interspersed around the different buttons?","index":319,"end_time":1354.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think that''s actually going to be more.","index":320,"end_time":1358.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1356.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s why I was kind of scrolling through the website that''s going to be more driven towards what our sections are.","index":321,"end_time":1364.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1358.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if this section is driven towards getting a demo, we''re going to have a demo link here.","index":322,"end_time":1369.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1364.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I want to have some sections where it actually shows features and talks about the different things that the software does for them.","index":323,"end_time":1379.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1370.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And in that way, in that section, we''ll have it as a needs consultation.","index":324,"end_time":1383.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1379.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''s reaching two different audiences or two.","index":325,"end_time":1387.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1385.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Two different minds essentially.","index":326,"end_time":1389.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1387.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you?","index":327,"end_time":1389.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1389.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":328,"end_time":1391.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1390.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think I understand what you''re saying, Natalie.","index":329,"end_time":1393.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1391.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do you want to design that or could do you want Keenan to help you design that?","index":330,"end_time":1399.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1393.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What he''s saying?","index":331,"end_time":1400.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1399.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And do you understand it?","index":332,"end_time":1401.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1400.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I understand.","index":333,"end_time":1402.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1401.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We can take the first stab at it and then send it over.","index":334,"end_time":1405.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1402.68,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":335,"end_time":1406.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what you''re saying, Keenan, is we''re going to have two different calendly links.","index":336,"end_time":1410.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1406.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":337,"end_time":1411.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1410.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"One that is for a demo, that''s the longer time.","index":338,"end_time":1413.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1411.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then the other one is a needs consultation.","index":339,"end_time":1415.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1413.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s just a couple of minutes.","index":340,"end_time":1417.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1415.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":341,"end_time":1418.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1417.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":342,"end_time":1419.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1418.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":343,"end_time":1419.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1419.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So they''ll be.","index":344,"end_time":1420.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1419.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''ll have a 30 minute and an hour option that they can click on.","index":345,"end_time":1424.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1420.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I doubt the user will.","index":346,"end_time":1426.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1424.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I doubt you''ll put that on the website.","index":347,"end_time":1427.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''ll probably just click on it and get the 30 minute or the hour.","index":348,"end_time":1430.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":349,"end_time":1431.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1431.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then you can change those calendar links however you want.","index":350,"end_time":1434.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1431.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":351,"end_time":1436.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1435.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":352,"end_time":1436.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1436.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It just makes that initial contact so then I can reach out to them and, and follow up.","index":353,"end_time":1441.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1436.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But.","index":354,"end_time":1443.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1442.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And just to give you a, a detail and an idea so it makes your work faster.","index":355,"end_time":1449.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1443.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, what I''m really looking for is this top section of the website.","index":356,"end_time":1453.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1449.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''d really.","index":357,"end_time":1454.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1453.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We want to identify kind of our hook and what that is.","index":358,"end_time":1459.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1455.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what a grip on does in a very quick effective term up here and then a few key points that are going to say what it does and why it''s so effective and then in another set.","index":359,"end_time":1474.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1459.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Real quick.","index":360,"end_time":1477.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1476.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I mean that''s good feedback.","index":361,"end_time":1479.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.739,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But.","index":362,"end_time":1480.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1479.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As they.","index":363,"end_time":1483.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1482.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''ve been attempting to do that we''ll need more specific feedback so we know what to put here.","index":364,"end_time":1490.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1483.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I have some.","index":365,"end_time":1492.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1491.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So by Monday.","index":366,"end_time":1493.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1492.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"By Monday, Natalie, I''m gonna send you.","index":367,"end_time":1496.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1493.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"A list of like these are the top one liners that we have that we''d like to utilize.","index":368,"end_time":1505.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1498.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"These are the features that we''d like to utilize.","index":369,"end_time":1508.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1506.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That way you guys can input them in the website in some of these key places.","index":370,"end_time":1513.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1508.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ll be very specific on this top section because it''s where we win business if they get to the website.","index":371,"end_time":1520.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1514.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":372,"end_time":1520.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1520.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I''ll be very specific of what I would like to see up here to, to give us a launch point.","index":373,"end_time":1526.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1521.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ll send that over to you guys by Monday.","index":374,"end_time":1529.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1527.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":375,"end_time":1530.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1530.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, this, this piece I love.","index":376,"end_time":1533.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1531.04,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think this view is great and I think it gives people a very real life hands on what this software does for us.","index":377,"end_time":1542.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1533.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then a section under here and I''ll be specific about this one as well.","index":378,"end_time":1548.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1544.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This homepage is probably where I''ll give a lot of direction and just some ideas on and, and not to take away, you know, what you guys do in your input as well.","index":379,"end_time":1557.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1548.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So feel free to not do exactly what it is.","index":380,"end_time":1561.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1558.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I want to give you what those talk points are and the specific features that we''d like to call out and so making some adjustments to some of these.","index":381,"end_time":1570.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1561.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"One of this sections on the homepage, this will be kind of features what the software does.","index":382,"end_time":1577.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1571.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Things are going to stand out to the different minds.","index":383,"end_time":1580.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1577.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that initial tag is going to be your executive that''s browsing in the morning, drinking coffee.","index":384,"end_time":1585.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1580.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They want the quick one liner of what this is doing for my business and how it''s going to affect me with some stats.","index":385,"end_time":1591.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1585.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is going to be more of your billing assistant that''s there.","index":386,"end_time":1596.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1592.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How does it affect my communication with my teams and allow coaching and things of those things of that nature.","index":387,"end_time":1602.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1596.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ve already taken some notes on those things.","index":388,"end_time":1604.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1602.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''ll want a section like that that maybe does a needs consultation.","index":389,"end_time":1609.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1606.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s kind of what I would like to see as far as some website ideas and just kind of where my brain is at today.","index":390,"end_time":1618.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1612.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m going to pause there and see Shane, if there''s anything that you want to make and adjustments to that or.","index":391,"end_time":1625.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1619.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, no, it sounds like a good approach.","index":392,"end_time":1630.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As I consider, you know, as you come on board and give us that feedback.","index":393,"end_time":1635.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1630.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"One of my questions is Keenan and Natalie, how will you guys work together?","index":394,"end_time":1641.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1636.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Natalie, I know you guys have a lot of things in the, in the hopper you''re working on and this is, this is probably a.","index":395,"end_time":1649.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1641.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Deviation from that with some kind of, you know, like a course correction potentially, for lack of a better term.","index":396,"end_time":1658.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1652.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How does that fit into your.","index":397,"end_time":1660.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1658.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like how do we fit this in?","index":398,"end_time":1664.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1662.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do we stop that other work and do this work?","index":399,"end_time":1667.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1664.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How do we, how do we do that.","index":400,"end_time":1669.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1667.489,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"From a workload perspective?","index":401,"end_time":1673.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1671.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean we can do it all at the same time, but I do want to put priority on this.","index":402,"end_time":1677.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1673.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":403,"end_time":1678.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1678.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I think, I mean the website is the main place we''re driving people so if we can improve it anyway, we should.","index":404,"end_time":1684.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1678.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":405,"end_time":1685.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1684.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":406,"end_time":1686.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1685.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then like I said, I''ll also send over some of the outbound material like the emails and ads that are currently launched so that we can get Keenan''s thoughts on that too.","index":407,"end_time":1697.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1686.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, so what you''re saying is, is that.","index":408,"end_time":1700.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1698.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''re going to try to do it in parallel.","index":409,"end_time":1703.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1701.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What?","index":410,"end_time":1703.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1703.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What?","index":411,"end_time":1704.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1704.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So my background is Agile software, meaning that we do Incrementally and get things out pretty quickly.","index":412,"end_time":1709.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1704.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t want to do a big bang where we spend a month and we get this all out.","index":413,"end_time":1716.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1712.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I would like to even do it as pieces.","index":414,"end_time":1718.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1716.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if we improve portions of the.","index":415,"end_time":1720.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1718.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Whatever we''re working on as we improve them and it''s ready to go, we should just go.","index":416,"end_time":1725.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1720.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":417,"end_time":1726.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1725.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then watch it kind of incrementally improve over time rather than, oh, now it''s all different.","index":418,"end_time":1730.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1726.2,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":419,"end_time":1731.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1731.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":420,"end_time":1732.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1731.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so it sounds like the two of you will work together to coordinate this effort is what I''m hearing.","index":421,"end_time":1740.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1733.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":1741.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1741.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":423,"end_time":1743.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1742.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And by the way, I think this is great feedback, Keenan.","index":424,"end_time":1750.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1745.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I''m excited to see this.","index":425,"end_time":1753.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1751.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I know that we''ve been.","index":426,"end_time":1754.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1753.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think what you bring to the table is just that.","index":427,"end_time":1756.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1754.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Focus on dental.","index":428,"end_time":1759.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1758.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think that as you are able to speak to the dental, that''s an area that I haven''t been able to accomplish.","index":429,"end_time":1765.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1759.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so this.","index":430,"end_time":1768.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1767.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This will improve the messaging.","index":431,"end_time":1771.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1768.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":432,"end_time":1775.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1774.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Dental.","index":433,"end_time":1775.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1775.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Dental is.","index":434,"end_time":1777.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1776.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s.","index":435,"end_time":1779.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s oddly simple and made to be way too difficult.","index":436,"end_time":1785.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1779.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And when you''re in that environment and you see the different people and the different segments, it''s one of those businesses where there''s just not enough communication that goes on.","index":437,"end_time":1795.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1785.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this brings that all together.","index":438,"end_time":1796.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1795.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think it''s an amazing solution for what they deal with on a daily basis and could solve a lot of problems and tension within an office.","index":439,"end_time":1805.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1797.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s why I was so excited to get involved with this.","index":440,"end_time":1809.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1806.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s really what I want the messaging to be.","index":441,"end_time":1811.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1809.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I want it to be clear in that way.","index":442,"end_time":1813.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1811.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so, you know, my history has been coaching.","index":443,"end_time":1817.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1814.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then on the sales side of this, your pitch deck, and you want that all to align.","index":444,"end_time":1823.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1817.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s important that if I send a customer to my website, that the pitch deck that I delivered to them has similar or same information on there.","index":445,"end_time":1833.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1823.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ve been in those situations as a salesperson where you''re in that demo or that conversation and they say, oh, well, I saw this somewhere else.","index":446,"end_time":1842.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1833.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then you''re trying to answer too many different questions during your demo and you''re not actually getting to what the product is.","index":447,"end_time":1850.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1842.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You want it to remain focused.","index":448,"end_time":1852.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1850.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s why the fluid messaging across everything that we''re doing I think.","index":449,"end_time":1856.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1852.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is key as we go forward.","index":450,"end_time":1859.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1857.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, I''m going to send you the one liners, the features, the things that stand out to me, and the things that I would like to remain as the focus of kind of this.","index":451,"end_time":1872.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1861.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Reset, I guess.","index":452,"end_time":1875.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1874.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then if you can send me the Information you have.","index":453,"end_time":1881.889,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1877.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"When can you send that to me?","index":454,"end_time":1883.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1882.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Actually, I''ll just ask you that so I can take the time to look through that too.","index":455,"end_time":1887.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1883.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can send it over to you today.","index":456,"end_time":1889.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1888.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":457,"end_time":1890.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1889.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If you send that over today, then I''ll have you know, the rest of the week and over the weekend to kind of look through it.","index":458,"end_time":1895.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1890.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I''ll add some thoughts for that email on Monday as well.","index":459,"end_time":1899.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1896.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If that works for you.","index":460,"end_time":1900.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1899.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":461,"end_time":1901.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1900.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":462,"end_time":1902.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1901.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Nate, I''ll.","index":463,"end_time":1904.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1903.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or Shane, I''ll send you that email as well.","index":464,"end_time":1908.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1904.38,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That way you have the communication to look through.","index":465,"end_time":1910.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1908.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then.","index":466,"end_time":1913.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1912.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That the one pagers, things like that were those created by your team, Natalie, or those things.","index":467,"end_time":1920.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1915.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That we are creating, the case studies were created by our team.","index":468,"end_time":1925.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1920.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":469,"end_time":1926.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1925.61,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll send those specifically to you as well because I think those serve a purpose and we still want to have those one pagers and some of that information.","index":470,"end_time":1937.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1928.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I think some, some adjustments on there can call out some information.","index":471,"end_time":1942.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1937.449,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":472,"end_time":1947.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1944.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And the LinkedIn post, Shane, that were from the past.","index":473,"end_time":1951.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1948.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Where was he getting his.","index":474,"end_time":1953.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1952.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"His information and art?","index":475,"end_time":1957.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1955.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just from the current marketing materials that we have.","index":476,"end_time":1959.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1957.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, usually out of his butt.","index":477,"end_time":1961.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1960.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it was just winded.","index":478,"end_time":1965.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1962.979,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Very, very winded.","index":479,"end_time":1966.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1965.5,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":480,"end_time":1966.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1966.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s.","index":481,"end_time":1967.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1966.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It was, it was absolute garbage.","index":482,"end_time":1970.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1968.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You can delete it.","index":483,"end_time":1971.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1970.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":484,"end_time":1972.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1972.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And Natalie, that''s, that''s kind of the direction and the idea at this point is to take some of the wind out of the information that we have.","index":485,"end_time":1981.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1973.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a lot of information and we really want to make it easy to see what we do and how a grip on impacts the day.","index":486,"end_time":1989.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1981.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":487,"end_time":1989.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1989.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How it impacts your billing team, how it impacts your providers.","index":488,"end_time":1994.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1989.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s things that I''ve experienced.","index":489,"end_time":1998.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1994.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I''ll try to be specific about the information I send you.","index":490,"end_time":2002.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1998.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Feel free at any point to say this doesn''t make sense, Keenan.","index":491,"end_time":2007.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2003.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or I think this, you know.","index":492,"end_time":2010.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2007.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":493,"end_time":2011.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2010.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I want your feedback, your expertise as well.","index":494,"end_time":2013.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2011.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I want it to be a working partnership.","index":495,"end_time":2015.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2014.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So if there''s something that you think you have to offer that can add to what we''re trying to do or that can bring the information together.","index":496,"end_time":2022.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2015.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":497,"end_time":2024.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2023.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Feel free to share that with me as, as we go through this as well.","index":498,"end_time":2028.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2024.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, sounds great.","index":499,"end_time":2030.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2029.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I would like to be this as much of a tweak as we possibly can instead of a revamp.","index":500,"end_time":2035.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2030.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Although I recognize the scope of it and that''s just a desire as we go through it, Keenan, you''ll probably see things that we can change slightly and get a big, big impact.","index":501,"end_time":2050.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2038.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''d like to focus on those small tweaks that Get a big impact first and then we''ll move into the more extensive.","index":502,"end_time":2058.089,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2051.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Changes as we need them.","index":503,"end_time":2061.369,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2060.009,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":504,"end_time":2062.449,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2061.929,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So the website and the homepage isn''t actually going to be as much of a tweak.","index":505,"end_time":2067.529,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2062.449,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s just going to be the information that''s in those sections is going to be the primary on there.","index":506,"end_time":2074.329,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2068.009,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s really what I want to do is kind of that facelift that changes that initial draw and getting them to click.","index":507,"end_time":2081.609,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2074.649,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that won''t be a ton of information that''s on there.","index":508,"end_time":2084.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2081.609,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Not, we''re not changing imagery and things like that too much.","index":509,"end_time":2087.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2084.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe replacing a report with a different picture or something like that.","index":510,"end_time":2091.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2088.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But most of it''s going to be what.","index":511,"end_time":2093.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2092,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What said, what''s the wording that we have on there is what we''re going to look at.","index":512,"end_time":2098.159,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2093.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that should be pretty small, I think, and incremental for us to be able to do.","index":513,"end_time":2102.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2098.159,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"With me owning the LinkedIn post, I think that gives some opportunity to start making some connections there as well.","index":514,"end_time":2110.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2104.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then I''ll take a look at the information that Natalie has and hopefully that doesn''t create too much work for what we''re trying to accomplish there either.","index":515,"end_time":2119.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2111.1,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But I won''t really have that answer until I can look through some of that information.","index":516,"end_time":2124.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2119.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, Natalie, you''re the professional on the marketing side, so I do want to take some time to just kind of hear from you of what challenges your team is facing or what you think the challenges are.","index":517,"end_time":2139.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2127.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Current state.","index":518,"end_time":2141.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2140.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So maybe I can kind of lean my.","index":519,"end_time":2144.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2142.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Lean my thoughts towards those as well.","index":520,"end_time":2146.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2145.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":521,"end_time":2148.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2148.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think what we''ve seen so far is a lot of engagement at the top of the funnel and we discussed this with Shane as well.","index":522,"end_time":2156.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2148.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''re sending out these campaigns through email as well.","index":523,"end_time":2160.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2156.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"As previously, we did LinkedIn, like, direct messages, so they would come from an Agrippon salesperson, send a connection request to a professional, and then LinkedIn ads.","index":524,"end_time":2171.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2160.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we saw good engagement there.","index":525,"end_time":2173.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2172.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, people click on the emails, get to the landing page, people clicked on the LinkedIn ads.","index":526,"end_time":2178.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2173.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We had a few people download some of the case studies.","index":527,"end_time":2182.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2178.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But what we''re.","index":528,"end_time":2185.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2184.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Our biggest challenge is getting them to take that next step of actually reaching out and scheduling a demo.","index":529,"end_time":2191.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2185.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s the biggest gap that we have right now.","index":530,"end_time":2194.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2192.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":531,"end_time":2195.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2195.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So any ideas that you have on how to reconcile, that would definitely be helpful.","index":532,"end_time":2200.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2195.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":533,"end_time":2204.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2203.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Shane, anything that you want to add to that or anything that.","index":534,"end_time":2207.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2204.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, we have a lot of activity and no, no, no revenue.","index":535,"end_time":2214.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2208.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":536,"end_time":2215.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2214.84,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Does that make sense?","index":537,"end_time":2216.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2215.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, we haven''t been able to Convert the finances.","index":538,"end_time":2218.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2216.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But if you look at the data, we got hundreds of people clicking on things and even taking the time to review it.","index":539,"end_time":2227.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2220.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But so far, I think we''ve had one demo.","index":540,"end_time":2231.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2228.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We weren''t able to close it, but we had one demo.","index":541,"end_time":2234.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2231.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":542,"end_time":2236.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2235.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I, I think, you know, just coming into this from an outsider''s perspective, I think gives a fresh set of eyes and I.","index":543,"end_time":2244.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2236.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Those were the things that stood out to me immediately, Especially coming into this thinking, you know, as a sales professional that''s going to demo this product, what are my key things?","index":544,"end_time":2255.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2244.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Because that''s where you.","index":545,"end_time":2257.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2256.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s where you sell it.","index":546,"end_time":2258.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2257.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right.","index":547,"end_time":2259.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2258.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If I step into an office here in town and say, hey, I just wanted to talk to you about something, and I have three minutes.","index":548,"end_time":2265.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2259.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What are the.","index":549,"end_time":2265.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2265.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Those three things?","index":550,"end_time":2266.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2265.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You know, what are the.","index":551,"end_time":2268.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2267.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s the message I can deliver in three minutes?","index":552,"end_time":2270.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2268.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s going to continue the conversation.","index":553,"end_time":2272.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2270.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And, and if we can put that on the website, on the ads, I think that''ll move us in the right direction.","index":554,"end_time":2278.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2272.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that''s where my, my focus really is.","index":555,"end_time":2280.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2278.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That works.","index":556,"end_time":2281.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2280.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, what kind of time frame does your team have.","index":557,"end_time":2285.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2282.56,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That we''re working with in this partnership?","index":558,"end_time":2289.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2287.279,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there anything I need to know as far as time frame or completion?","index":559,"end_time":2294,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2289.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The way you know your timeframe for handling projects.","index":560,"end_time":2297.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2294.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''d say it''s usually on a case by case basis.","index":561,"end_time":2301.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2299.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But for most things, we have a maximum of a week turnaround time.","index":562,"end_time":2305.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2301.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So say, for example, we''re standing up a new landing page.","index":563,"end_time":2309.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2306.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We can promise that we''ll have that done for you within a week.","index":564,"end_time":2313.769,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2310.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":565,"end_time":2315.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2314.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":566,"end_time":2316.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2315.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Any specific.","index":567,"end_time":2318.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2317.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Format for communication?","index":568,"end_time":2321.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2320.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Any.","index":569,"end_time":2322.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2321.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Any.","index":570,"end_time":2322.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2322.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Any needs from me specifically to make this easier for your team for you?","index":571,"end_time":2328.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2323.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":572,"end_time":2330.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2329.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we communicate mostly via email with Shane, so that works pretty well.","index":573,"end_time":2335.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2330.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''m happy to keep doing that.","index":574,"end_time":2336.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2335.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We also do have this tool called Markup, which Shane has used as well, which it allows us to upload documents there so that you can easily leave feedback on it just through comments.","index":575,"end_time":2347.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2337.16,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So that just makes it easier, like say, for a landing page or ads, instead of sending you an actual PDF, we send you that link and then you can just write comments on specific parts.","index":576,"end_time":2359.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2348.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So when I''m sending over the marketing materials that we have, I can do it in that format as well, just so it''s easier for you to leave feedback.","index":577,"end_time":2367.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2360.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s perfect.","index":578,"end_time":2369.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2368.94,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay, that''s great.","index":579,"end_time":2371.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2370.22,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''ll work.","index":580,"end_time":2371.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2371.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Shane, as far as, you know, the marketing materials, the sales materials, everything that we have, current state.","index":581,"end_time":2382.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2373.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I know you said, you know, take it, do what you need to with it make those adjustments.","index":582,"end_time":2389.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2384.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Are there things that you have anybody signing off on, any sort of legal official.","index":583,"end_time":2397.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2390.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Am I sending these things to Natalie''s team after the fact overview or is this you?","index":584,"end_time":2403.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2397.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You are.","index":585,"end_time":2404.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2403.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I appreciate the.","index":586,"end_time":2406.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2405.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"How should I say that?","index":587,"end_time":2409.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2408.48,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The favorable view that you have of our company?","index":588,"end_time":2413.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2409.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, I wouldn''t say that there''s much of any legal or there''s very little process of.","index":589,"end_time":2420.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2414.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Of protection, so to speak, to make sure we have the right message.","index":590,"end_time":2425.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2422.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just make it as truthful as you can.","index":591,"end_time":2429.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2426.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, obviously don''t want to get into sending people any false claims or anything, but.","index":592,"end_time":2434.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2429.6,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, no, we''re not gonna, I''m not gonna.","index":593,"end_time":2437.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2435.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That is, I don''t think we''re at that point yet in our company to worry about that kind of thing.","index":594,"end_time":2442.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2438.81,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":595,"end_time":2443.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2443.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Well, that''s where I''ve been with Verizon in the past.","index":596,"end_time":2446.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2443.73,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":597,"end_time":2446.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2446.25,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"No, they wanted to control the message and, and, and honestly, the way I look at it, you are the control of the message.","index":598,"end_time":2453.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2446.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I trust you.","index":599,"end_time":2454.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2453.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Go forward, do good things.","index":600,"end_time":2456.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2454.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":601,"end_time":2457.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2456.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We haven''t been sued yet.","index":602,"end_time":2459.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2457.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So, Natalie, just to make sure that my mind is aligning on where we''re at and what we''re doing.","index":603,"end_time":2471.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2463.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I can see your team''s perspective, can you share just a couple of things with me, like the things that stand out as far as your projects, just to give me a view into your world a little bit?","index":604,"end_time":2482.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2473.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, let me.","index":605,"end_time":2485.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2483.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll open up the full.","index":606,"end_time":2487.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2486.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That we have.","index":607,"end_time":2488.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2488.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":608,"end_time":2511.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2510.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So a few examples.","index":609,"end_time":2513.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2512.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So one of the main things that we do is these ABM campaigns, account based marketing campaigns where we have a list of companies that we want to target and then we try to get in front of them through a variety of different channels.","index":610,"end_time":2528.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2514.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So one of those being email, we send direct emails to contacts, LinkedIn paid campaigns as well as LinkedIn direct messages.","index":611,"end_time":2538.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2529.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I can show an example of some of the email sequences that we''re sending out and then I''ll add all of this to the folder as well so you can take a, a deeper look.","index":612,"end_time":2551.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2541.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":613,"end_time":2552.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2552.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":614,"end_time":2553.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2552.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You can see all the emails that we''re sending out and take a look at them.","index":615,"end_time":2555.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2553.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":616,"end_time":2556.589,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2555.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":617,"end_time":2557.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2556.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this one was a free trial offer that we just started.","index":618,"end_time":2561.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2557.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So like we mentioned, we have those top of the funnel contacts who are doing a bunch of activity but not converting.","index":619,"end_time":2567.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2561.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We then entered them into another email sequence where we''re offering them a free trial of a grip on.","index":620,"end_time":2573.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2568.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s one thing I wanted to mention and that Keenan, you probably want to look at.","index":621,"end_time":2579.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2574.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They have data on who''s clicking What?","index":622,"end_time":2581.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2579.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And it''s a different level.","index":623,"end_time":2583.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2582.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Sometimes we see the individual.","index":624,"end_time":2585.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2583.8,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"For example, on LinkedIn, we know who clicked, we don''t see.","index":625,"end_time":2589.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2585.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And on emails, some emails we click.","index":626,"end_time":2592.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2590.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But if they go directly to the website, we don''t really know.","index":627,"end_time":2594.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2592.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We kind of know companies and that kind of thing.","index":628,"end_time":2596.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2594.72,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think it would be worthwhile to show you some of that data and then give you access to it so you can, you can study it and see what we should do with it.","index":629,"end_time":2603.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2597.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":630,"end_time":2605.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2604.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s, I''m guessing that''s housed with your team, Natalie?","index":631,"end_time":2607.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2605.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes, they share it with us.","index":632,"end_time":2610.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2608.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, if that''s, if that''s available.","index":633,"end_time":2612.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2610.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That would be amazing.","index":634,"end_time":2614.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2612.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":635,"end_time":2615.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2615.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And we can even pull up a little bit and introduce it to you here, if you want.","index":636,"end_time":2620.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2616.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes.","index":637,"end_time":2622.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2622.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":638,"end_time":2625.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2625.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we have a couple of tools that we use.","index":639,"end_time":2629.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2625.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"To try and identify people that are.","index":640,"end_time":2633.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2631.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Visiting the website.","index":641,"end_time":2636.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2635.45,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":642,"end_time":2640.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2640.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is one, for example.","index":643,"end_time":2644.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2643.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this is a tool that we use called Factors, which identifies companies that are visiting the agrippon website.","index":644,"end_time":2651.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2644.33,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So it''ll identify the company name, their domain, which URLs they visited and on what date.","index":645,"end_time":2658.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2652.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I did see some data that shows you, like how many people visited or how many times they visited.","index":646,"end_time":2665.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2659.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe it''s on another tab.","index":647,"end_time":2667.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2665.63,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I, I did that manually.","index":648,"end_time":2669.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2667.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Oh, thank you.","index":649,"end_time":2671.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2670.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I thought it was valuable.","index":650,"end_time":2672.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2671.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":651,"end_time":2673.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2672.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Here.","index":652,"end_time":2673.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2673.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we just count the number of times they actually came to the site.","index":653,"end_time":2677.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2674.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Now set 47 for a company of 5,000 people, but 17 for a company of 50 people.","index":654,"end_time":2687.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2679.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s interesting.","index":655,"end_time":2689.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2688.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Right?","index":656,"end_time":2689.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2689.14,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So.","index":657,"end_time":2690.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2689.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":658,"end_time":2690.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2690.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":659,"end_time":2693.899,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2693.539,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that, that tells you that, I mean, they''re looking for something.","index":660,"end_time":2698.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2693.899,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They''re looking for some sort of solution to something they''re doing today.","index":661,"end_time":2701.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2698.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And this gives me the ability to be proactive and then, you know, reach out directly as well.","index":662,"end_time":2708.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2702.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so, yeah, this information is huge.","index":663,"end_time":2712.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2709.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"If this, if, if I can get access to this, that would be, that''d be amazing.","index":664,"end_time":2717.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2712.89,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":665,"end_time":2718.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2717.93,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this actually kind of ties into the conversation we started with about Salesforce because this, I think without us, you know, making fiscal changes, this actually gives us access to some of that same information that you would get in some of that Salesforce format, Natalie.","index":666,"end_time":2738.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2718.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I think this is valuable for me as far as back end information because it gives me things I can work on as well.","index":667,"end_time":2745.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2738.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Even if it''s, you know, one phone call that says this is why we didn''t move forward or this is why we didn''t connect, that helps us grow and take the next step.","index":668,"end_time":2753.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2745.19,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so this, as the sales lead in a situation like this, this is extremely valuable to Me.","index":669,"end_time":2760.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2754.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So any of this information that you can share or give me access to would be greatly appreciated.","index":670,"end_time":2767.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2760.75,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":671,"end_time":2768.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2768.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Great.","index":672,"end_time":2769.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2768.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":673,"end_time":2769.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2769.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we do this on a weekly basis, create a new spreadsheet, just looking back on the past week.","index":674,"end_time":2775.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2769.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And then we also look at email clicks.","index":675,"end_time":2778.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2775.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So of all the sequences that are going out, which contacts are clicking on.","index":676,"end_time":2783.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2778.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Which links and, and how many times some people click multiple times.","index":677,"end_time":2788.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2783.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You were showing me that data too.","index":678,"end_time":2789.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2788.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, like this one.","index":679,"end_time":2791.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2790.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"This is a lot of information.","index":680,"end_time":2793.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2791.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So at the end of the month, what we do is look back on all the weeks and then see who are the top engaged contacts that are worth reaching out to.","index":681,"end_time":2800.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2793.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That would be amazing.","index":682,"end_time":2802.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2801.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And I think.","index":683,"end_time":2803.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2802.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Have we gotten that for November?","index":684,"end_time":2804.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2803.17,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t think we have.","index":685,"end_time":2808.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2806.85,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Maybe we have.","index":686,"end_time":2812.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2811.09,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, it looks like we have.","index":687,"end_time":2814.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2813.01,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Did you send this to me?","index":688,"end_time":2816.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2815.65,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think so.","index":689,"end_time":2818.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2817.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I can reset.","index":690,"end_time":2818.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2818.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":691,"end_time":2819.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2818.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Please do.","index":692,"end_time":2820.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2819.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":693,"end_time":2820.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2820.42,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So Natalie, with this information here, when you guys gather this information at the end of the month, look at that.","index":694,"end_time":2830.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2823.54,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Somebody even clicked the calendar.","index":695,"end_time":2832.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2830.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like they came so close.","index":696,"end_time":2836.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2834.9,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is it, is, is she active right now?","index":697,"end_time":2838.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2836.66,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is the calendar going to somebody today?","index":698,"end_time":2840.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2838.78,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s a concern, isn''t it?","index":699,"end_time":2843.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2842.02,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"You''d have to connect with, with, with Monique and say, is anybody.","index":700,"end_time":2851.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2844.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":701,"end_time":2852.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2852.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Do we know when they clicked on it?","index":702,"end_time":2854.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2852.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think, honestly, I think when she left, I think she just left.","index":703,"end_time":2858.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2854.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":704,"end_time":2859.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2858.88,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":705,"end_time":2860.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2860.24,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''ll send you those two links.","index":706,"end_time":2862.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2860.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Immediately today.","index":707,"end_time":2866.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2865.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ll send those over to you and.","index":708,"end_time":2868.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2866.52,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And you can also reach out and say, hey.","index":709,"end_time":2870.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2868.44,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We see that you.","index":710,"end_time":2873.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2872.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I don''t know if when you click on that you actually got to fill it out or whatever, but those are people probably should reach out to directly.","index":711,"end_time":2881.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2873.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":712,"end_time":2881.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2881.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so just so you know, Shane, I''ve also taken a list of anybody that showed up in the email before any of those leads.","index":713,"end_time":2887.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2881.83,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And at the point that I feel like I''m ready for, you know, head on conversations, I''m going to reach back out to those people as a first offer of, hey, this is where we''re at today.","index":714,"end_time":2902.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2888.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"These are some of the updates that we''ve made and try to regroup those contacts as well.","index":715,"end_time":2906.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2902.21,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Love it.","index":716,"end_time":2908.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2907.53,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Speaking of updates, I get emails when people click the.","index":717,"end_time":2912.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2908.97,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"The demo schedule demo and they fill it out.","index":718,"end_time":2916.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2914.49,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I get the email.","index":719,"end_time":2917.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2916.57,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I got one recently, but it wasn''t, wasn''t anything.","index":720,"end_time":2920.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2917.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Natalie, can we add Keenan to those somehow?","index":721,"end_time":2925.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2921.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, probably through Zoho post.","index":722,"end_time":2926.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2925.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Need to put his email on there or something.","index":723,"end_time":2928.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2926.86,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yep.","index":724,"end_time":2929.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2929.06,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I''m absolutely an information guy.","index":725,"end_time":2933.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2931.7,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"When I drink my coffee in the morning, I''ll look through all the emails and Just see what''s there, and I might.","index":726,"end_time":2939.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2934.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"May ping you like this information specifically here.","index":727,"end_time":2942.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2939.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So when you guys gathered this information at the end of the month, Natalie, is your team doing anything specific to these 10?","index":728,"end_time":2950.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2942.74,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yes, these ones get entered into that nurture sequence for the free trial offer.","index":729,"end_time":2955.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2951.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Okay.","index":730,"end_time":2957.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2957.23,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":731,"end_time":2958.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2958.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I love seeing this, and this is kind of one of the reasons I wanted to kind of dive into your world a little bit so that what.","index":732,"end_time":2969.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2964.03,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What you''d get section with the bullet points.","index":733,"end_time":2971.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2969.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think there''s some great bullet points in there.","index":734,"end_time":2975.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2973.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think sometimes it''s just a wording tweak that we can make that really applies to what they''re trying to accomplish.","index":735,"end_time":2982.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2975.11,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"They may get more reaction out of it.","index":736,"end_time":2985.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2983.79,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So I''m excited to see this.","index":737,"end_time":2988.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2986.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think we have a lot of potential in the things we already have with just some small adjustments and tweaks as far as our messaging.","index":738,"end_time":2995.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2988.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And that''s really what I''m looking at.","index":739,"end_time":2997.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2995.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So this is greatly helpful for me and what I''m trying to accomplish so we can.","index":740,"end_time":3004.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2997.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we can get some.","index":741,"end_time":3006.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3005.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Get some excitement, some action involved in what we''re trying to do.","index":742,"end_time":3009.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3006.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there.","index":743,"end_time":3012.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3011.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there anything, Natalie, that.","index":744,"end_time":3014.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3012.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Anything back of my.","index":745,"end_time":3017.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3015.99,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Or front of my back of mind, anything that''s hanging on you that you think if this was an adjustment we could make, this would change things for us?","index":746,"end_time":3026.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3017.47,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there anything like that, that.","index":747,"end_time":3028.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3026.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That you''re holding on to.","index":748,"end_time":3029.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3028.27,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And you can think through that?","index":749,"end_time":3034.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3033.76,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I. I know that was.","index":750,"end_time":3036,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3034.92,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That.","index":751,"end_time":3036.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3036.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s.","index":752,"end_time":3037.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3036.64,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s kind of a.","index":753,"end_time":3037.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3037.08,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"A broad question.","index":754,"end_time":3038.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3037.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But the reason I asked that is sometimes in these partnerships, you feel like there''s a direction things are going and you''re trying to meet that direction for a customer, but you feel like if there were small changes going in a different direction, maybe that would open things up.","index":755,"end_time":3052.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3038.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And so I just want you to kind of have that question back of mind as you''re sending me information over, and if there''s something that stands out to you that you think, you know what, I think this could happen.","index":756,"end_time":3063.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3053.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think this could change things.","index":757,"end_time":3065.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3063.95,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Don''t hesitate.","index":758,"end_time":3067.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3066.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just.","index":759,"end_time":3067.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3067.07,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just send it over.","index":760,"end_time":3068.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3067.39,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That''s.","index":761,"end_time":3070.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3069.67,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I mean, that''s kind of what I''m doing today, right.","index":762,"end_time":3072.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3070.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is looking through everything and saying, I think these tweaks can get us in the right direction.","index":763,"end_time":3077.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3072.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I definitely want you to feel like this is that type of working partnership where you can say, I tried something the other day.","index":764,"end_time":3084.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3077.43,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I think this could be effective, and let''s partner in some things and.","index":765,"end_time":3089.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3084.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And make it exciting.","index":766,"end_time":3090.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3089.51,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":767,"end_time":3092.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3091.91,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll think on it.","index":768,"end_time":3093.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3092.31,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"One other project I forgot to mention is Shane does a podcast as well.","index":769,"end_time":3099.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3093.59,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So he''s done a couple of episodes so far and they just talk about, like, common challenges within the dental space.","index":770,"end_time":3106.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3100.15,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But something that we have been trying recently is reaching out to dental practice consultants who have a portfolio of clients that they help and essentially if we could get in partnership with them, basically helping them recommend a grip on to their clients.","index":771,"end_time":3124,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3106.87,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So what we''ve been trying to do is invite some of those consultants to be guests on the podcast.","index":772,"end_time":3129.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3124.96,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Shane, how did the most recent one go?","index":773,"end_time":3133.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3131.28,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Was it Sandy?","index":774,"end_time":3134.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3133.4,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It''s a great question.","index":775,"end_time":3135.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3134.32,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She was awfully weird.","index":776,"end_time":3136.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3135.36,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"That went nowhere.","index":777,"end_time":3138.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3137.12,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She.","index":778,"end_time":3139.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3139.26,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She was.","index":779,"end_time":3140.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3139.58,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"She asked some really strange questions and then she decided it wasn''t a good fit.","index":780,"end_time":3144.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3140.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we''re done.","index":781,"end_time":3144.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3144.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Like, okay.","index":782,"end_time":3146.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3145.18,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Just.","index":783,"end_time":3148.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3147.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"It was an odd conversation.","index":784,"end_time":3150.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3148.34,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I was like, at the end of it, I was like, just scratching my head.","index":785,"end_time":3153.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3150.46,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":786,"end_time":3157.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3155.82,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So podcasts would be new to me.","index":787,"end_time":3158.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3157.3,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"I''ve never been involved in a podcast before, but.","index":788,"end_time":3161.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3158.62,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But definitely something we need to get you.","index":789,"end_time":3164.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3161.98,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We need to get you and Brad on one to introduce you in the company and then.","index":790,"end_time":3169.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3164.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But that''s what needs to happen.","index":791,"end_time":3172.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3171.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But what.","index":792,"end_time":3173.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3172.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"What''s great about it is, is that they edit it and they do all the things and make it publishable.","index":793,"end_time":3177.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3173.05,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"So we just get on a talk.","index":794,"end_time":3178.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3177.37,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Perfect.","index":795,"end_time":3179.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3179.29,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have.","index":796,"end_time":3184.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3183.69,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"And when.","index":797,"end_time":3185.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3184.41,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Wednesdays are usually the best for that, but.","index":798,"end_time":3187.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3185.13,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"But it''s hard to find time in everybody''s schedule.","index":799,"end_time":3190.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3187.77,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Yeah.","index":800,"end_time":3191.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3191.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"We have about seven minutes left.","index":801,"end_time":3195.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3193.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Want to be respectful.","index":802,"end_time":3197.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3196.55,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Everybody''s time.","index":803,"end_time":3198.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3197.71,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Is there anything.","index":804,"end_time":3199.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3198.35,"speaker_name":null},{"text":"Any final words, final notes, any.","