"start_time":3126.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Which number are we looking for?","index":1030,"end_time":3132.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3130.89,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"A teeny little green number?","index":1031,"end_time":3135.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3133.29,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"It is 36.","index":1032,"end_time":3138.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3136.65,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"There we go.","index":1033,"end_time":3139.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3139.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"At least that''s what it looks like to me.","index":1034,"end_time":3142.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3140.97,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I can make my.","index":1035,"end_time":3144.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3142.73,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I can magnify my screen, too.","index":1036,"end_time":3145.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3144.05,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"36 or 38.","index":1037,"end_time":3149.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3147.61,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"One of those.","index":1038,"end_time":3150.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3149.79,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, 36.","index":1039,"end_time":3151.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3150.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s right.","index":1040,"end_time":3153.47,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3152.75,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yes.","index":1041,"end_time":3153.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3153.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You were yay.","index":1042,"end_time":3154.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3153.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":1043,"end_time":3156.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3155.55,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":1044,"end_time":3157.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3156.67,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And for the.","index":1045,"end_time":3157.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3157.03,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Rachel, I really appreciated your text on the.","index":1046,"end_time":3160.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3158.67,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"The dropping of the podcast.","index":1047,"end_time":3162.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3160.87,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"The podcast for Meg, because then I saw it super timely, and then I promoted, and then I told her, amazing.","index":1048,"end_time":3171.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3162.75,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":1049,"end_time":3173.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3173.47,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"If I''ve got the leader on text, it''s a good.","index":1050,"end_time":3176.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3173.83,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"It''s a good way to do it.","index":1051,"end_time":3180.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3179.83,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"However, Meg''s mom is in the hospital, so she''s not promoting today.","index":1052,"end_time":3185.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3180.95,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Oh, no.","index":1053,"end_time":3186.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3185.35,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, she just sent me a text.","index":1054,"end_time":3188.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3186.95,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She''s okay.","index":1055,"end_time":3189.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3188.95,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Meg is lovely.","index":1056,"end_time":3191.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3190.39,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"She is lovely.","index":1057,"end_time":3193.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3192.31,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She has trouble with herself on video.","index":1058,"end_time":3196.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3193.23,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She''s like, this is a big cringe for me.","index":1059,"end_time":3197.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3196.07,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And I was like, well, you don''t have to watch it, but it''s good.","index":1060,"end_time":3200.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3197.71,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Just listen.","index":1061,"end_time":3201.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3200.51,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"But you did great.","index":1062,"end_time":3202.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3202.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She did do great.","index":1063,"end_time":3204.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3203.24,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She''s so sweet.","index":1064,"end_time":3205.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3204.24,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah, no, she''s.","index":1065,"end_time":3206.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3206.04,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She''s great at it.","index":1066,"end_time":3207.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3206.92,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She just.","index":1067,"end_time":3208.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3207.76,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"She doesn''t like to watch herself.","index":1068,"end_time":3209.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3208.12,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And I''m like, me neither.","index":1069,"end_time":3210.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3209.68,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I remember.","index":1070,"end_time":3212.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3211.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I remember those first couple of recordings.","index":1071,"end_time":3214.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3212.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nancy, you.","index":1072,"end_time":3215.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3214.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You were a little nervous, but I told you you were going to be great.","index":1073,"end_time":3218.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3215.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I just.","index":1074,"end_time":3219.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3218.76,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I just can''t watch it too much.","index":1075,"end_time":3221.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3219.8,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"That''s why Rachel and Julia does do so much of the heavy lift in that, because I just can''t.","index":1076,"end_time":3227.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3221.72,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I. I can''t take in the content because I''m busy looking at, like, my weird hair or whatever.","index":1077,"end_time":3235.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3230.05,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":1078,"end_time":3236.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3235.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When I.","index":1079,"end_time":3236.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3236.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When I''m guesting on some of our internal shows, I just go live with it, guys.","index":1080,"end_time":3241.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3236.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t even want to look at it.","index":1081,"end_time":3242.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3241.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":1082,"end_time":3245.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3244.21,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"It''s.","index":1083,"end_time":3246.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3245.69,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Let me know if it''s any good.","index":1084,"end_time":3247.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3246.09,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Right?","index":1085,"end_time":3247.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3247.17,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":1086,"end_time":3247.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3247.41,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Was that everything from our.","index":1087,"end_time":3251.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3249.81,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"